il%20may%20seem%20insignificant%20to%20some%2C%20but%20I%20find%20it%20makes%20using%20the%20tool%20so%20much%20more%20pleasant.%20If%20I%20have%20to%20contort%20my%20body%20to%20be%20able%20to%20use%20a%20hair%20dryer%20properly%2C%20chances%20are%20I%20won't%20use%20it%2C%20but%20Shark's%20user-friendly%20design%20makes%20me%20reach%20for%20this%20one%20often.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EActually%20using%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-63063-20%26h%3D391acd7b06aadc9dee1444c92395aecb0e281453b79b611c1742693be71dd15a%26postID%3D65579abf00482b84e83dd698%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fstyle%252Fshark-flexstyle-review%26site%3Din%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.sharkclean.com%252Fproducts%252Fbuild-your-own-shark-flexstyle-zidHD400%253F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFlexStyle%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20seamless%20process.%20I%20give%20my%20hair%20a%20rough%20dry%20with%20the%20blow%20dryer%20and%20then%20snap%20in%20my%20favorite%20attachment%2C%20usually%20the%20oval%20brush%20or%20styling%20concentrator.%20I%20like%20to%20use%20the%20lowest%20heat%20and%20the%20highest%20airflow%20to%20get%20fast%20results%20without%20damaging%20my%20strands.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20will%20amp%20the%20heat%20up%20a%20bit%20if%20I'm%20going%20for%20a%20super%20styled%20look%2C%20like%20a%20sleek%20mane%20with%20the%20paddle%20brush%20or%20bouncy%20curls%20with%20the%20auto-wrap%20curlers%2C%20but%20I've%20noticed%20that%20using%20the%20highest%20heat%20setting%20on%20my%20fine%20hair%20for%20a%20whole%20styling%20session%20usually%20leaves%20my%20strands%20looking%20a%20bit%20more%20frizzy%20and%20less%20shiny.%20If%20maximum%20shine%20and%20softness%20are%20your%20goal%2C%20always%20make%20sure%20to%20set%20the%20style%20with%20the%20cool%20shot%20too.%20There's%20something%20magical%20in%20there.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Salon-quality%20results%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20salon-qua