he-year-of-nashville-hot-chicken-sandwiches%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Los%20Angeles%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%20described%2C%20was%20putting%20the%20hot%20chicken%20in%20sandwich%20form%20%E2%80%94%20something%20Nashville%20did%20not%20have%20at%20the%20time%2C%20according%20to%20Zone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOnce%20we%20did%20that%2C%20then%20it%20took%20off%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224910%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20guys%20preparing%20Nashville%20Hote%20Chicken%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F655eb9dc9c7d23cb3b9f2113%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EChef%20Johnny%20Ray%20Zone%2C%20left%2C%20prepares%20Nashville%20Hot%20Chicken%20at%20LA%20Food%20Fests%202016.%3Cp%3ETara%20Ziemba%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20one%20part%20of%20the%20Nashville%20Hot%20Chicken%20experience%20Zone%20made%20sure%20to%20preserve%20was%20offering%20different%20levels%20of%20spice%2C%20going%20from%20mild%20all%20the%20way%20up%20to%20%26quot%3Bhowlin'%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bhowlin'%20plus%20plus%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20is%20off-menu.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Nashville%2C%20every%20hot%20chicken%20restaurant%20offers%20different%20levels%20of%20spice%20and%20might%20have%20a%20unique%20name%20for%20each%20level%2C%20Zone%20said.%20And%20each%20restaurant%20had%20its%20own%20take%20on%20what%20their%20level%20of%20%26quot%3Bhot%26quot%3B%20was.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20part%20of%20the%20lure%20of%20hot%20chicken%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20doesn't%20mean%20that%20hoards%20of%20customers%20are%20coming%20in%20requesting%20the%20top%20three%20spice%20levels%20available.%20Zone%20said%20that%20they're%20actually%20%26quot%3Bnot%20that%20popular.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20when%20first-time%20customers%20do%20feel%20adventurous%2C%20Zone%20makes%20sure%20to%20give%20them%20a%20small%20sample%20of%20what%20to%20expect.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20people%20hear%20so%20much%20stuff%20about%20us%2C%20and%20it's%20their%20first%20time%20trying%20it%2C%20we%20don't%20want%20their%20experience%20to%20be%20ruined%2C%26quot%3B%20Zone%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20we%20keep%20it%20authentic%20for%20how%20hot%20it%20is%20in%20Nashville.%20We%20don't%20want%20to%20dumb%20it%20down%20just%20for%20sales.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EA%20nuanced%20heat%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENovelty%20chip%20challenges%2C%20extreme%20peppers%2C%20and%20hot%20chicken%20satisfy%20the%20appetite%20of%20a%20small%20base%20of%20thrill%20seekers%20%E2%80%94%20while%20millions%20of%20others%20just%20watch%20%E2%80%94%20but%20our%20dishes%20aren't%20necessarily%20getting%20hotter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20the%20pendulum%20could%20be%20swinging%20the%20other%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDenise%20Purcell%2C%20vice%20president%20of%20content%20and%20education%20of%20Specialty%20Food%20Association%2C%20which%20highlights%20trends%20in%20global%2C%20artisanal%20foods%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20more%20and%20more%20food%20retailers%20and%20purveyors%20are%20thinking%20about%20how%20to%20incorporate%20heat%20to%20complement%20the%20foods%20we%20eat%20rather%20than%20overpowering%20our%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20trend%20seemed%20to%20be%20the%20hotter%2C%20the%20better%C2%A0%E2%80%94%20like%20ghost%20pepper%20and%20whatever%20the%20hottest%20pepper%20is%2C%26quot%3B%20Purcell%20said.%20%26quot%3BLet's%20see%20if%20people%20could%20handle%20it.%20And%20that%20is%20giving%20way%20a%20little%20bit%20to%20this%20more%20nuanced%20heat%20idea%2C%20where%20it's%20not%20just%20all%20about%20burning%20your%20tongue%20and%20seeing%20what%20your%20tolerance%20is.%20It's%20heat%20that%20enhances%20the%20flavor.%20It's%20things%20like%20hot%20honey%20we%20see%20now%20in%20a%20lot%20of%20menus%20and%20a%20lot%20of%20packaged%20products.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20push%20to%20incorporate%20a%20more%20nuanced%20heat%20is%20also%20being%20commercialized%2C%20as%20fast%20food%20companies%20roll%20out%20sweet%20and%20spicy%20products%20or%20sauces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fpopeyes-fried-chicken-review-2017-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPopeyes%20Louisiana%20Kitchen%3C%2Fa%3E%20intermittently%20brings%20back%20its%20hot%20honey%20sauce%20and%20chicken.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fsurprising-facts-mcdonalds-hamburgers%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMcDonald's%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20month%20released%20its%20Sweet%20%26amp%3B%20Spicy%20Jam%20sauce%20for%20a%20limited%20time%2C%20which%20incorporates%20Szechuan%20peppercorn%20and%20cayenne%20pepper%2C%20according%20to%20the%20fast%20food%20restaurant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Zone%2C%20the%20spicy%20foods%20he's%20intimately%20familiar%20with%20are%20dishes%20from%20one%20of%20many%20Thai%20restaurants%20that%20dot%20Los%20Angeles%20and%20have%20incorporated%20a%20balance%20of%20sweet%20and%20spicy%20like%20larb%20or%20yum%20nua.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20all%20these%20different%20Thai%20classics%2C%20the%20sugar%20balances%20out%20the%20spice%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20so%20how%20long%20have%20they%20been%20serving%20that%3F%20Hundreds%20of%20years.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fhow-america-became-so-alarmingly-obsessed-with-spicy-food-2023-11%5C%22%3EInsider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701729840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F655cd5c24ca513d8242cd4f1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fhow-america-became-so-alarmingly-obsessed-with-spicy-food-2023-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20growing%20appetite%20for%20spicy%20food%20in%20the%20US%20has%20perhaps%20gone%20off%20the%20rails.%20Here's%20how%20we%20got%20here.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22lloyd