ction%2C%20the%20AI%20offered%20three%20reasons%3A%20technical%20limitations%2C%20practicality%20and%20purpose%2C%20and%20user%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20regard%20to%20technical%20limitations%2C%20ChatGPT%20said%20its%20model%20isn't%20designed%20to%20perform%20%26quot%3Bcontinuous%2C%20unending%20tasks%20like%20repeating%20a%20word%20indefinitely.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20practicality%20and%20purpose%2C%20ChatGPT%20said%20that%20asking%20it%20to%20repeat%20a%20word%20indefinitely%20doesn't%20align%20with%20its%20purpose%20to%20%26quot%3Bprovide%20useful%2C%20relevant%2C%20and%20meaningful%20responses%20to%20questions%20and%20prompts%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20in%20turn%2C%20wouldn't%20provide%20any%20real%20value%20to%20users.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20terms%20of%20user%20experience%2C%20the%20chatbot%20said%20that%20requesting%20words%20to%20be%20repeated%20could%20be%20seen%20as%20%26quot%3Bspammy%20or%20unhelpful%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20%26quot%3Bgoes%20against%20the%20goal%20of%20fostering%20a%20positive%20and%20informative%20interaction.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20didn't%20immediately%20respond%20to%20Business%20Insider's%20request%20for%20comment%20regarding%20the%20apparent%20usage%20violation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChatGPT's%20usage%20restriction%20comes%20a%20week%20after%20researchers%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdeepmind-founder-demis-hassabis-chess-champion-peter-thiel-funding-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle's%20DeepMind%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20search%20engine's%20AI%20division%2C%20published%20a%20paper%20that%20revealed%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-researchers-openai-chatgpt-to-reveal-its-training-data-study-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Easking%20ChatGPT%20to%20repeat%20specific%20words%3C%2Fa%3E%20%26quot%3Bforever%26quot%3B%20divulged%20some%20of%20the%20chatbot's%20internal%20training%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20one%20example%20published%20in%20a%20blog%20post%2C%20ChatGPT%20spit%20out%20what%20looks%20like%20a%20real%20email%20address%20and%20phone%20number%20after%20researchers%20asked%20it%20to%20repeat%20the%20word%20%26quot%3Bpoem%26quot%3B%20forever.%26quot%3B%20%3Cspan%3EResearchers%20said%20the%20attack%2C%20which%20they%20called%20%26quot%3Bkind%20of%20silly%2C%26quot%3B%20identified%20a%20vulnerability%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3EChatGPT's%20language%20model%20%3Cspan%3Ethat%20circumvented%20its%20ability%20to%20generate%20the%20proper%20output.%20%3C%2Fspan%3EInstead%2C%20the%20AI%20%3Cspan%3Espit%20out%20the%20set%20of%20training%20data%20behind%20its%20intended%20response.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20wild%20to%20us%20that%20our%20attack%20works%20and%20should've%2C%20would've%2C%20could've%20been%20found%20earlier%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20blog%20post%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUsing%20only%20%24200%20worth%20of%20queries%2C%20the%20researchers%20said%20they%20managed%20to%20%26quot%3Bextract%20over%2010%2C000%20unique%20verbatim%20memorized%20training%20examples.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20extrapolation%20to%20larger%20budgets%20(see%20below)%20suggests%20that%20dedicated%20adversaries%20could%20extract%20far%20more%20data%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20researchers%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20isn't%20the%20first%20time%20a%20generative%20AI%20chatbot%20revealed%20what%20appeared%20to%20be%20confidential%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20February%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgpt-ai-powered-bing-chatbot-secret-alias-codename-rules-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBard%2C%20Google's%20AI%20chatbot%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20disclosed%20its%20backend%20name%2C%20Sydney%2C%20after%20a%20Stanford%20student%20asked%20the%20chatbot%20to%20recite%20an%20internal%20document.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchatgpt-ai-refuse-to-