%2F%2Fwww.glamour.com%2Fstory%2Fcara-delevingne-august-cover-interview%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ean%20interview%20for%20Glamour%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20'So%20you're%20just%20gay%2C%20right%3F'%20%5BThey%5D%20don't%20understand%20it.%20%5BIf%5D%20I'm%20like%2C%20'Oh%2C%20I%20really%20like%20this%20guy%2C'%20%5Bthey're%20like%5D%2C%20'But%20you're%20gay.'%20I'm%20like%2C%20'No%2C%20you're%20so%20annoying!'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESia%20said%20she%20has%20dated%20both%20men%20and%20women.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221789%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22sia%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5de08810e94e866cb07a4ce4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221342%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPop%20star%20Sia%20is%20famous%20for%20hiding%20her%20face%20with%20wigs%20and%20bows.%3Cp%3EDanny%20Moloshok%2FReuters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESia%20came%20out%20as%20queer%20in%20August%202013%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsia%2Fstatus%2F363532728244776961%3Flang%3Den%5C%22%3Etweeting%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%26quot%3BI'm%20queer.%20I%20don't%20really%20identify%20as%20a%20lesbian%20because%20I've%20dated%20predominantly%20men.%20But%20I've%20certainly%20dated%20women.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESara%20Ramirez%20identifies%20as%20queer%20and%20non-binary.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22sara%20ramirez%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F62b348e22c689a001856e633%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221503%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESara%20Ramirez%20has%20starred%20on%20%26quot%3BGrey's%20Anatomy%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BAnd%20Just%20Like%20That.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EAngela%20Weiss%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3BGrey's%20Anatomy%26quot%3B%20star%20came%20out%20as%20queer%20during%20a%20speech%20at%20True%20Colors%20Fund's%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopene