0Miller%20%2F%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ECho%20said%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.huffingtonpost.com%2Fentry%2Fmargaret-cho-bisexuality-pride_us_5b27b980e4b0783ae12b754e%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%202018%20interview%20with%20Huffington%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20she's%20not%20sure%20if%20bisexual%20is%20necessarily%20the%20right%20word%2C%20%26quot%3Bbecause%20that%20indicates%20that%20there's%20only%20two%20genders%2C%20and%20I%20don't%20believe%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20been%20with%20people%20all%20across%20the%20spectrum%20of%20gender%20and%20who%20have%20all%20kinds%20of%20different%20expressions%20of%20gender%2C%20so%20it's%20so%20hard%20to%20say%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20continued.%20%26quot%3BMaybe%20'pansexual'%20is%20technically%20the%20more%20correct%20term%20but%20I%20like%20'bisexual'%20because%20it's%20kind%20of%20'70s.%20%5BLaughs%5D%20There's%20something%20very%20chic%20about%20that%20word%20and%20I%20guess%20that's%20probably%20the%20right%20one%20for%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EJulianne%20Hough%20told%20her%20husband%20she's%20%26quot%3Bnot%20straight.%26quot%3B%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22769%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Julianne%20Hough%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5bc4bd93a5a15c1093771829%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22577%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJulianne%20Hough%20is%20an%20actress%20and%20dancer.%3Cp%3EAngela%20Weiss%2FGetty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20Women's%20Health%20Magazine%2C%20Hough%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.womenshealthmag.com%2Flife%2Fa28451746%2Fjulianne-hough-naked-strength-interview%2F%5C%22%3Esaid%20she%20told%20her%20husband%20that%20she%20wasn't%20straight%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20many%20fans%20interpreted%20as%20her%20speaking%20out%20against%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gl