.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65302b1dbe9edfa8eda3fe18%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EGrace%20Cary%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAs%20we%20age%2C%20it%20becomes%20harder%20for%20our%20bodies%20to%20absorb%20nutrients.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESupplements%20like%20vitamin%20D%20or%20magnesium%20may%20be%20in%20order.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20experts%20say%C2%A0%26quot%3Bdo%20not%20just%20take%20things%26quot%3B%C2%A0without%20knowing%20what%20your%20body%20needs.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EDr.%20Nir%20Barzilai%20says%20supplements%20are%20definitely%2C%20unequivocally%20improving%20the%20health%20of%20one%20thing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSupplements%20are%20really%20good%20for%20the%20economy%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20director%20of%20the%20Institute%20for%20Aging%20Research%20at%20the%20Albert%20Einstein%20College%20of%20Medicine%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20supporting%20a%20lot%20of%20companies%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20workers%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ibisworld.com%2Findustry-statistics%2Fmarket-size%2Fvitamin-supplement-manufacturing-united-states%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520market%2520size%252C%2520measured%2520by%2Cdeclined%2520%252D3.5%2525%2520in%25202022.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eroughly%20%2439%20billion%20global%20supplement%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20market.%20But%20whether%20they're%20supporting%20our%20health%20is%20a%20murkier%2C%20more%20challenging%20question%20to%20answer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20aging%2C%20Barzilai%2C%20and%20other%20leading%20longevity%20experts%20say%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsupplement-expert-doesnt-take-supplements-eats-vegan-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20supplement%20regimen%20you%20should%20choose%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20live%20a%20long%2C%20healthy%20life%20won't%20be%20one%20single%2C%20straightforward%20routine.%20It%20should%20be%20unique%20to%20each%20person%2C%20and%20each%20moment%20in%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20should%20be%20driven%20by%20the%20biology%20of%20your%20body%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr.%20Andrea%20Maier%2C%20who%20co-directs%20the%20Centre%20for%20Healthy%20Longevity%20at%20the%20National%20University%20of%20Singapore%2C%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BDo%20not%20just%20take%20things.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaier's%20own%20research%20has%20shown%20her%20that%20many%20supplements%20are%20not%20living%20up%20to%20their%20label%20claims%2C%20and%20that%20everyone%20reacts%20a%20little%20differently%20to%20each%20pill%20they%20pop.%20Though%20she%20does%20recommend%20supplements%20to%20some%20of%20her%20patients%20at%20private%20and%20public%20longevity%20clinics%20in%20Singapore%2C%20she%20also%20takes%20a%20very%20personal%20and%20scientific%20approach%20to%20the%20task%20of%20prescribing%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20our%20body's%20ability%20to%20absorb%20nutrients%20diminishes%20as%20we%20age%2C%20it%20is%20true%20that%20supplements%20may%20help%20some%20people%20improve%20their%20longevity%20in%20certain%20ways%2C%20if%20taken%20judiciously.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20five%20of%20the%20buzziest%20science-backed%20supplements%20around%2C%20and%20what%20they%20may%20do%20for%20aging%20bodies%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EVitamin%20D%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222100%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22older%20woman%20enjoying%20sunshine%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F656df5a158e7c0c29a29306c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221400%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAngelo%20Cavalli%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20supplement%20is%20taken%20by%20a%20long%20list%20of%20aging%20and%20longevity%20experts%2C%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fvitamin-d-and-longevity-anti-aging-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eimmunologist%20Anthony%20Fauci%2C%20to%20the%20biohacker%20who%20wants%20to%20live%20forever%2C%20Bryan%20Johnson%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Vitamin%20D%20is%20essential%20for%20our%20bone%20density%2C%20helping%20us%20convert%20calcium%20into%20strength.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGenerally%2C%20we%20absorb%20most%20of%20our%20vitamin%20D%20from%20the%20sun%2C%20so%20many%20people%20choose%20to%20supplement%20their%20vitamin%20D%20intake%20in%20the%20wintertime%2C%20when%20we%20aren't%20getting%20as%20many%20rays%20outside.%20But%20you%20can%20also%20get%20vitamin%20D%20from%20a%20diet%20rich%20in%20fatty%20fish%20like%20salmon%2C%20as%20well%20as%20fortified%20milk%2C%20and%20egg%20yolks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBarzilai%20says%20that%20even%20though%20his%20vitamin%20D%20levels%20are%20low%2C%20he%20doesn't%20supplement%20this%20nutrient.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20only%20thing%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D1023d51c671ae7f20a54ea24dbaa661b67c5d964b48ddd0fe6747754d7868806%26postID%3D656de23533f7fba9f6408e66%26postSlug%3D5-supplements-for-longevity-and-anti-aging-expert-recommendations-2023-12%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.nature.com%252Farticles%252Fs41574-021-00593-z%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Evitamin%20D%20helps%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fods.od.nih.gov%2Ffactsheets%2FVitaminD-Consumer%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DTaking%2520vitamin%2520D%2520and%2520calcium%2520supplements%2520slightly%2520increases%2520bone%2520strength%2520in%2520older%2520adults%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eosteoporosis%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%2C%20he%20says%20bone%20scans%20suggest%20%26quot%3Bmy%20bones%20are%20really%20thick%2C%26quot%3B%20so%20he%20doesn't%20think%20he%20needs%20to%20supplement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EFish%20oil%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222100%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22omega%203%20rich%20foods%2C%20including%20salmon%2C%20avocado%2C%20walnuts%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F656df8f97a3c8094d5d93307%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221401%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESalmon%2C%20avocados%2C%20and%20walnuts%20are%20all%20rich%20in%20omega-3%20fatty%20acids.%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFish%20oil%20is%20a%20great%20heart%20health%20protector%2C%20providing%20plenty%20of%20omega-3%20fatty%20acids%20to%20help%20improve%20cholesterol.%20There's%20some%20evidence%20it's%20also%20good%20for%20preventing%20and%20improving%20the%20swelling%20and%20pain%20of%20arthritis%2C%20through%20some%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2F7639807%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eanti-inflammatory%20properties%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20you%20can%20also%20get%20plenty%20of%20omega-3s%20from%20eating%20walnuts%2C%20salmon%2C%20or%20tuna.%20Eating%20your%20omega-3s%20in%20fish%20and%20nuts%20makes%20it%20easier%20to%20pack%20in%20a%20whole%20host%20of%20other%20nutrients%20too.%20Nuts%2C%20for%20example%2C%20are%20a%20great%20source%20of%20fiber%2C%20magnesium%2C%20and%20vitamin%20B6%2C%20while%20salmon%20is%20great%20for%20improving%20vitamin%20D%20stores%20and%20vitamin%20B12.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ENAD%2B%20boosters%2C%20like%20NR%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22person%20running%20in%20the%20cold%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F639c99b1b67d300019e7de84%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3Eamriphoto%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ENicotinamide%20adenine%20dinucleotide%20(NAD%2B)%20is%20a%20key%20enzyme%20that%20our%20body%20uses%20to%20create%20energy.%20It%20can%20help%20maintain%20tissue%20health%2C%20keep%20DNA%20repaired%2C%20and%20improve%20immune%20function%20and%20metabolism.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20nicotinamide%20riboside%20(NR)%20and%20nicotinamide%20mononucleotide%20(NMN)%20are%20precursors%20that%20may%20help%20us%20produce%20more%20NAD%2B%2C%20and%20they%20have%20become%20popular%20anti-aging%20supplements.%20But%20last%20year%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.regulations.gov%2Fdocument%2FFDA-2022-S-0023-0051%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EUS%20Food%20and%20Drug%20Administration%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20that%20because%20NMN%20is%20being%20investigated%20as%20a%20drug%2C%20it%20%26quot%3Bmay%20not%20be%20marketed%20as%20or%20in%20a%20dietary%20supplement.%26quot%3B%20NR%20is%20still%20allowed%20to%20be%20sold%20as%20a%20supplement%2C%20and%20some%20studies%20have%20suggested%20that%20it%20has%20decent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.science.org%2Fdoi%2F10.1126%2Fsciadv.adi4862%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eanti-inflammatory%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20properties%20that%20can%20help%20support%20healthy%20aging.%20More%20NR%20studies%20are%20needed%20targeting%20populations%20with%20NAD%2B%20deficiencies%20to%20know%20for%20sure%20what%20benefits%20the%20supplement%20might%20provide%20to%20those%20who%20could%20potentially%20use%20it%20the%20most.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EFisetin%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Strawberries.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F62a8d2f46053710019ea3624%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EStrawberries%20get%20their%20bright%20red%20hue%20from%20a%20chemical%20compound%20called%20fisetin.%20This%20polyphenol%20can%20have%20some%20great%20anti-inflammatory%20properties%20too.%3Cp%3EIvan%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20chemical%20compound%2C%20naturally%20occurring%20in%20brightly-hued%20strawberries%2C%20persimmons%2C%20onions%2C%20and%20apples%2C%20is%20a%20great%20inflammation%20fighter%20that%20may%20help%20clear%20out%20old%2C%20toxic%20cells%20that%20build%20up%20as%20we%20age.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Flongevity-researcher-takes-strawberry-antioxidant-fisetin-healthy-aging-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ELongevity%20researcher%20Paul%20Robbins%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20says%20he%20takes%20it%20every%20two%20weeks%2C%20and%20his%20%26quot%3Bcranky%26quot%3B%20knee%20always%20feels%20better%20afterwards.%20Other%20aging%20researchers%20are%20excited%20about%20the%20potential%20of%20fisetin%20to%20improve%20conditions%20as%20varied%20as%20arthritis%20and%20Alzheimer's.%20But%20many%20experts%20caution%20people%20to%20wait%20a%20few%20years%2C%20until%20more%20is%20known%20about%20the%20benefits%20and%20risks%20of%20popping%20it%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMagnesium%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222100%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22salt%2C%20dead%20sea%20israel%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F656dfc430ec98e92f74bb187%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221400%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Dead%20Sea%20is%20rich%20in%20magnesium%2C%20which%20is%20a%20key%20component%20for%20saltwater.%3Cp%3EScience%20Photo%20Library%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMagnesium%20is%20a%20kind%20of%20wonder%20mineral%20for%20the%20body%20%E2%80%94%20great%20for%20maintaining%20healthy%20muscles%2C%20bones%2C%20nerves%2C%20blood%20pressure%2C%20and%20cellular%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fsupplements-peter-attia-takes-longevity-anti-aging-magnesium-vitamin-d-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ELongevity%20doctor%20Peter%20Attia%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20pops%20several%20different%20kinds%20of%20magnesium%20every%20day%2C%20to%20promote%20healthy%20aging.%20But%20you%20can%20already%20get%20a%20lot%20of%20magnesium%20just%20from%20eating%20a%20healthful%20plant-based%20diet%20full%20of%20dark%20leafy%20greens%20like%20spinach%2C%20bananas%2C%20avocados%2C%20nuts%2C%20and%20beans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EFine-tune%20your%20diet%20and%20exercise%20routine%20before%20you%20try%20supplements%2C%20experts%20say%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226720%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Red%20chilli%20and%20bean%20soup.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6267bfda784b4d0019463961%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224480%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELongevity%20experts%20recommend%20adding%20more%20vegetables%2C%20beans%2C%20nuts%2C%20and%20seeds%20into%20your%20diet.%20%3Cp%3EGetty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20single%20supplement%20protocol%20all%20aging%20experts%20endorse.%20Instead%2C%20they%20universally%20agree%20that%20a%20healthy%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvegan-diet-better-for-health-than-omnivore-identical-twins-study-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplant-heavy%20diet%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20rich%20in%20nuts%2C%20legumes%2C%20fruits%20and%20vegetables%2C%20will%20serve%20aging%20bodies%20very%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20yet%2C%20in%20the%20US%2C%20more%20than%20half%20of%20American%20adults%20still%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cdc.gov%2Fnchs%2Fproducts%2Fdatabriefs%2Fdb399.htm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Etake%20some%20supplements%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Maier%20believes%20that's%2C%20in%20large%20part%2C%20to%20help%20ease%20anxiety.%20By%20buying%20a%20pill%2C%20we%20can%20feel%20like%20we're%20taking%20charge%20of%20our%20health%20In%20a%20country%20where%20there%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flongevity-drug-for-dogs-moves-closer-to-fda-approval-loyal-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eno%20drug%20that's%20ever%20been%20FDA%20approved%20for%20anti-aging%3C%2Fu%3E