thy's%20The%20Casual%20Clog%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20pair%20of%20Rothy's%20Casual%20Clogs%20in%20the%20color%20Merino%20Wool%2C%20Soft%20Black.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64f8e8db56f5190019fc8023%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ERothy's%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20may%20not%20imagine%20recycled%20plastic%20water%20bottles%20as%20the%20place%20to%20start%20for%20a%20pair%20of%20comfortable%20slippers%20for%20women%2C%20and%20neither%20did%20the%20INSIDER%20team%20%E2%80%94%20until%20we%20tried%20what%20we%20now%20consider%20some%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Fbest-flats%5C%22%3Ebest%20flats%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20eco-conscious%2C%20super%20flexible%20knit%20is%20Rothy's%20signature%20across%20their%20entire%20collection%20of%20shoes%20and%20totes%2C%20and%20requires%20no%20break-in%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Casual%20Clog's%20upper%20was%20made%20with%20a%20blend%20of%20five%20recycled%20water%20bottles%20and%20Responsible%20Wool%20Standard%20certified%20Merino%20wool.%20Their%20cushioned%20footbeds%20provide%20ample%20arch%20support%20and%20they%20have%20a%20wide%20toe%20box%2C%20perfect%20for%20those%20who%20like%20to%20wear%20thick%20socks%20with%20slippers.%20These%20clogs%20are%20perfect%20for%20around%20the%20house%2C%20but%20can%20just%20as%20easily%20be%20dressed%20up%20to%20wear%20out.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3ERead%20more%20in%20our%20full%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Frothys-flats-review%5C%22%3ERothy's%20flats%20review%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20luxury%3A%20Sleeper%20Lulu%20Shearling%20Slippers%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221426%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Pair%20of%20green%20Sleeper%20Lulu%20Shearling%20Slippers%20with%20pom%20pom%20details.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%