0noting%20that%20cashmere%20can%20get%20pretty%20toasty%2C%20so%20they'll%20be%20great%20in%20colder%20seasons%2C%20but%20not%20as%20ideal%20in%20warmer%20climates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20for%20wide%20feet%3A%20Acorn%20Spa%20Wrap%20Slide%20Slipper%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20baby%20blue%20quilted%20terrycloth%20slipper.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64cc19ce0b651c00193a58a7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22750%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAcorn%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20can%20be%20tough%20to%20find%20any%20shoe%20that%20properly%20fit%20wide%20feet%2C%20let%20alone%20a%20specific%20category%20of%20shoe%2C%20but%20the%20Acorn%20Spa%20Wrap%20Slipper%20was%20designed%20to%20fit%20%3Cem%3Eall%3C%2Fem%3E%20feet.%20Judging%20from%20the%20reviews%2C%20it%20does.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fuzzy%20spa-like%20house%20shoe%20is%20made%20from%20a%20washable%20terry%20material%20(as%20spa%20lounge%20accessories%20usually%20are)%20and%20features%20an%20adjustable%20wrap%20strap%2C%20ensuring%20the%20slipper%20fits%20a%20wide%20array%20of%20feet%20shapes%20and%20sizes.%20It%20also%20features%20the%20brand's%20patented%20multilayer%20Cloud%20Contour%E2%84%A2%20footbed%2C%20which%20offers%20the%20wearer%20optimal%20comfort%20and%20support.%20Acorn's%20size%20inclusivity%20earns%20them%20their%20spot%20among%20the%20best%20slippers%20for%20women%2C%20offering%20their%20Spa%20Wraps%20in%20small%20to%20extra%20large%2C%20including%20wide-specific%20sizes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20for%20narrow%20feet%3A%20Birkenstock%20Zermatt%20Shearling%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221066%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Birkenstock%20Zermatt%20Wool%20slipper%20in%20light%20rose%20color.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F643043cf3007470019fe2126%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EBirkenstock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20can%20be%20just%20as%20challenging%20to%20find%20women's%20slippers%20for%20narrow%20feet%20as%20wide%20feet%2C%20but%20luckily%20this%20pair%20from%20Birkenstock%20offers%20a%20solution.%20The%20true-to-size%20slip%20is%20constructed%20from%20Zermatt%20wool%20felt%20and%20its%20anatomically%20contoured%20cork-latex%20footbed%20is%20removable.%20Shearling%20lining%20makes%20the%20women's%20slipper%20extra%20cozy%2C%20and%20a%20grippy%20outsole%20prevents%20wearers%20from%20slipping%20or%20tripping.%20While%20the%20pair%20is%20on%20the%20pricier%20side%20(currently%20retailing%20for%20%2499.95)%2C%20with%20Birkenstock%20you%20can%20rest%20assured%20you're%20getting%20what%20you%20pay%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20trendy%3A%20UGG%20Fluff%20Yeah%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Pair%20of%20UGG%20Fluff%20Yeah%20Fuzz%20Slides%20in%20bright%20orange.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F643049e93007470019fe21d3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EUGG%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20on%20the%20hunt%20for%20a%20slipper%20that%20balances%20function%20and%20fashion%2C%20look%20no%20further%20than%20UGG's%20Fluff%20Year%20women's%20slipper.%20The%20slide%20is%20fuzzy%2C%20warm%2C%20and%20super%20trendy%3B%20we've%20seen%20the%20pair%20all%20over%20Instagram%20and%20TikTok%20and%20it's%20no%20secret%20why.%20Not%20only%20is%20this%20slipper%20perfect%20for%20at-home%20lounging%2C%20but%20it%20comes%20in%20over%2020%20colorways%20and%20funky%20prints%20to%20choose%20from.%20Functional%20features%20include%20100%25%20sheepskin%20for%20warmth%2C%20a%20rubber%20sole%20for%20stability%20and%20durability%2C%20plus%20an%20elastic%20strap%20to%20keep%20feet%20snug%20and%20in%20place.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3ERead%20our%20full%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Fugg-slippers-review%5C%22%3EUGG%20slippers%20review%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWhat%20to%20look%20for%20when%20shopping%20for%20women's%20slippers%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20nationally-renowned%20podiatrist%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20nofollow%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiipgf_102717_best-slippers-women-20%26h%3D3d8aedc4a10aaa81daddccef2c1a4a9e97e5d0c24469da76f4097bc37174b3ae%26postID%3D61b8efc7f2a36b1ac9f41fd0%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fstyle%252Fbest-slippers-women%26site%3Din%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.vionicshoes.com%252Fvionic-innovation-lab%252Fdr-jackie-sutera%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDr.%20Jackie%20Sutera%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20wearing%20slippers%20is%20a%20kind%20of%20%26quot%3Bactive%20recovery%26quot%3B%20for%20your%20feet%2C%20so%20the%20pair%20you%20wear%20the%20most%20must%20be%20both%20comfortable%20and%20supportive.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWalking%20and%20standing%20barefoot%20for%20long%20periods%20can%20cause%20pain%20over%20time%20for%20most%20people%2C%20especially%20on%20hard%20floors%2C%26quot%3B%20Sutera%20tells%20INSIDER.%20%26quot%3BSlippers%20also%20can%20be%20shock%20absorbing.%20They%20can%20come%20in%20many%20styles%20like%20those%20with%20a%20thong%2C%20open%2C%20closed%2C%20moccasin%2C%20slip-ons.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20shopping%20for%20your%20perfect%20fit%2C%20Sutera%20recommends%20starting%20by%20researching%20brands%20whose%20slippers%20feature%20design%20details%20like%20a%20contoured%20footbed%2C%20support%2C%20and%20cushion%20(her%20personal%20favorite%20is%20Vionic).%20Function%20should%20come%20first%2C%20then%20you%20can%20worry%20about%20your%20style%20preferences.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20you%20press%20%26quot%3Badd%20to%20cart%2C%26quot%3B%20Sutera%20stresses%20that%20thin%20and%20flat%20styles%20that%20offer%20little%20to%20no%20support%20are%20a%20no-go%3A%20%26quot%3BThese%20types%20are%20not%20fo