ng%20table.%20He%20later%20joined%20Congress%20as%20an%20MP%20from%20Mizoram.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22PRABIN%20KALITA%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fmizorams-man-of-the-moment-was-on-indiras-security-detail%2Farticleshow%2F105736059.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kamal%20Nath%20Asked%20To%20Quit%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20Congress%20Chief%20Post%3A%20Sources%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EKamal%20Nath%20--%20former%20Chief%20Minister-turned-Madhya%20Pradesh%20Congress%20chief%20--%20has%20been%20asked%20to%20step%20down%20from%20the%20post%2C%20sources%20said%20a%20day%20after%20the%20party%20got%20decimated%20in%20a%20state%20they%20were%20sure%20of%20winning.%20The%20results%20yesterday%20showed%20the%20BJP%20had%20won%20163%20of%20the%20state's%20230%20seats%20--%20more%20than%20double%20the%20Congress%20tally%20of%2066.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20figures%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20the%20situation%20could%20not%20be%20further%20from%20the%20Congress%20reading%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%2C%20led%20by%20Mr%20Nath%2C%20was%20convinced%20that%20there%20was%20huge%20anti-incumbency%20against%20the%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20convinced%20of%20victory%20was%20the%20party%20that%20on%20the%20morning%20of%20the%20counting%20day%2C%20posters%20came%20up%20congratulating%20Mr%20Nath%20on%20his%20victory.%20By%20noon%2C%20they%20had%20to%20be%20pulled%20down%20as%20the%20BJP%20established%20a%20comfortable%20lead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20party%20being%20convinced%20that%20anti-incumbency%20against%20the%20BJP%20would%20push%20the%20election%20in%20their%20direction%2C%20the%20Congress%20campaign%20strategy%20lacked%20an%20edge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20did%20not%20hold%20massive%20protests%20against%20the%20BJP%20to%20register%20its%20presence.%20The%20number%20of%20public%20meetings%20and%20rallies%20they%20held%20was%20almost%20half%20that%20of%20the%20BJP.%20This%20affected%20communication%20with%20the%20voters%20and%20made%20the%20party%20unable%20to%20carry%20its%20message%20across%2C%20leaders%20confided%20in%20private.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Nath's%20other%20move%20--%20denying%20the%20promised%20five%20to%20seven%20seats%20to%20INDIA%20bloc%20partner%20Samajwadi%20Party%20--%20has%20earned%20it%20the%20wrath%20of%20the%20alliance%20partners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20of%20seats%20at%20the%20state%20level%20was%20expected%20to%20be%20the%20blueprint%20for%20the%20bloc's%20one-on-one%20strategy%20for%20next%20year's%20general%20elections%20--%20dubbed%20a%20do-or-die%20battle%20with%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Congress%20has%20not%20been%20able%20to%20understand%20the%20ground%20situation%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%20What%20harm%20could%20have%20happened%20if%20they%20had%20given%205-7%20seats%20to%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%3F%20What%20have%20they%20won%20now%3F%26quot%3B%20National%20Conference%20chief%20Omar%20Abdullah%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20news%20agency%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJudging%20the%20results%20of%20INDIA%20alliance%20in%20the%20state%20elections%2C%20if%20the%20situation%20is%20like%20this%20in%20the%20future%2C%20we%20cannot%20win%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20reporters%20yesterday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20said%20the%20Congress%20could%20have%20won%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20and%20Rajasthan%2C%20but%20%26quot%3Bsome%20votes%20were%20cut%20by%20INDIA%20parties%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20truth.%20We%20had%20suggested%20a%20seat-sharing%20arrangement.%20They%20lost%20because%20of%20division%20of%20votes%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20the%20state%20assembly%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20Congress%20leader%20Manickam%20Tagore%20underscored%20the%20importance%20of%20allia