2%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fananya-panday-siddhant-chaturvedi-surprise-fans-at-nh7-weekender%2Farticleshow%2F105735672.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Cyclone%20Michaung%20To%20Make%20Landfall%20In%20Andhra%20Soon%2C%205%20Dead%20In%20Chennai%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESpeaking%20to%20NDTV%2C%20the%20Director%20General%20of%20the%20India%20Meteorological%20Department%2C%20Mrutyunjay%20Mohapatra%20said%20the%20windspeeds%20as%20of%209%20pm%20on%20Monday%20were%2090-100%20km%20per%20hour%20near%20the%20centre%20of%20the%20cyclone%20and%2070-80%20km%20per%20hour%20along%20the%20Nellore%20and%20Prakasam%20districts%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BThe%20system%20is%20moving%20northwards%2C%20therefore%20the%20windspeeds%20near%20Chennai%2C%20Thiruvallur%20and%20Kanchipuram%20districts%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%20are%20decreasing%20gradually%20and%20are%20around%2050-60%20km%20per%20hour.%20They%20will%20further%20decrease%20near%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20coast.%20This%20will%20increase%20gradually%20(in%20Andhra%20Pradesh)%20and%2C%20from%20midnight%2C%20the%20windspeed%20may%20be%2090-100%20km%20per%20hour%20between%20Nellore%20and%20Machilipathnam%20and%20it%20will%20continue%20till%20forenoon%20(morning)%20on%20Tuesday%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EA%20severe%20cyclonic%20storm%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20cause%20uprooting%20of%20small%20and%20medium%20trees%2C%20large-scale%20damage%20to%20hutments%20and%20mud%20houses%2C%20and%20partial%20damage%20to%20telephone%20and%20electric%20poles.%20It%20will%20also%20cause%20inundation%20and%20flooding%2C%20as%20has%20already%20happened%20in%20north-coastal%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20especially%20Chennai.%20Mr%20Mohapatra%20warned%20that%20cities%20and%20towns%20along%20coastal%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20will%20see%20extremely%20heavy%2C%20and%20even%20exceptionally%20heavy%20(30-40%20cm)%2C%20rainfall.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EA%20storm%20surge%2C%20or%20tidal%20wave%2C%20of%201-1.5%20metres%20is%20expected%20to%20inundate%20the%20low-lying%20areas%20of%20south%20coastal%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20the%20peak%20storm%20surge%20will%20be%20over%20the%20Bapatla%20and%20Krishna%20districts.%20The%20cyclone%20is%20expected%20to%20make%20landfall%20as%20a%20severe%20cyclonic%20storm%20with%20a%20maximum%20sustained%20wind%20speed%20of%2090-100%20km%20per%20hour%2C%20gusting%20to%20110%20km%20per%20hour.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EChennai%20saw%20five%20rain-related%20deaths%20on%20Monday.%20Two%20people%20died%20of%20electrocution%20while%20one%20was%20killed%20after%20a%20tree%20fell%20on%20him%20in%20the%20upmarket%20Besant%20Nagar%20area%20of%20the%20city%2C%20the%20Chennai%20Police%20said%2C%20according%20to%20news%20agency%20PTI.%20Two%20unidentified%20bodies%20of%20a%20man%20and%20a%20woman%20have%20been%20found%20in%20different%20rain-affected%20parts%20of%20the%20city.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThere%20is%20hope%2C%20however%2C%20for%20Chennai%20and%20the%20Greater%20Chennai%20area%20-%20which%20have%20seen%20flooding%20and%20large-scale%20power%20cuts%20-%20with%20the%20situation%20expected%20to%20improve%20after%2012%20am%20on%20Tuesday.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20not%20expecting%20extremely%20heavy%20rainfall%20after%20midnight%20and%20only%20heavy%20rainfall%2C%20and%20isolated%20very%20heavy%20rainfall%2C%20can%20be%20expected.%20The%20rainfall%20intensity%20and%20windspeed%20will%20decrease%20as%20the%20cyclone%20is%20moving%20away%20from%20Chennai.%20The%20windspeed%20will%20decrease%20from%2050-60%20km%20per%20hour%20to%2035-45%20km%20per%20hour%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Mohapatra%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Chennai%20airport%20will%20remain%20shut%20till%209%20am%20on%20Tuesday%20and%20the%20state%20government%20has%20also%20declared%20a%20public%20holiday%20for%20the%20Chennai%2C%20Chengalpattu%2C%20Kancheepuram%20and%2