%2C%20he%20thanked%20his%20Uber%20driver%20who%20relentlessly%20tried%20to%20reach%20his%20location%20to%20drive%20him%20to%20the%20airport.%C2%A0He%20wrote%2C%C2%A0''Special%20shoutout%20to%20%40Uber_India%20driver%20Prakash%20-%20absolute%20hero%20-%20tried%20to%20get%20to%20me%20for%20half%20hour%20through%20various%20routes%20driving%20almost%2010%20kms%20before%20I%20gave%20up%2C%20he%20didn't.%20Do%20rate%20%2F%20reward%20him%20well%2C%20I%20did%20send%20a%20tip%20via%20GPay.%20The%20app%20should%20allow%20rating%2Ftips%20even%20for%20cancellation.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20internet%20users%20enquired%20why%20he%20stepped%20out%20despite%20warnings%20from%20authorities.%20Mr%20Ganesh%20replied%20saying%20that%20he%20had%20a%20big%20client%20meeting%20in%20Mumbai.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20user%20wrote%2C%20''No%20matter%20whats%20important%20work%20always%20follow%20weather%20updates%20or%20at%20least%20follow%20many%20handles%20in%20X%20to%20get%20updates%20on%20weather.%20Don't%20venture%20out%20it's%20not%20safe.%20Let%20this%20a%20lesson%20who%20takes%20it%20lightly..%20and%20do%20follow%20my%20weather%20updates%20buddies...%20Stay%20safe.''%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20commented%2C%20''You%20should%20have%20planned%20well%20given%20the%20circumstances.%20Stay%20safe.%20I%20hope%20the%20Uber%20driver%20is%20safe%20at%20home.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20authorities%20have%20declared%20a%20public%20holiday%20today%20and%20tomorrow%2C%20shutting%20schools%20and%20colleges%20across%20the%20city%2C%20and%20dispatched%20rescue%20teams%20to%20avert%20any%20untoward%20incidents.%C2%A0Operations%20at%20the%20Chennai%20airport%20have%20been%20suspended%20till%209%20am%20tomorrow%20-%20with%20about%2070%20flights%20canceled%20due%20to%20flooding%20of%20the%20runway%20and%20tarmac%2C%20the%20Airport%20Authority%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701712500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F20