r%201%2C200%20Israelis%20and%20more%20than%2014%2C000%20Palestinians%20have%20been%20killed%20in%20the%20last%20two%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20open%20letter%20to%20UNSC%2C%20MSF%20International%20president%20Christos%20Christou%20writes%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20writing%20to%20you%20on%20behalf%20of%20M%C3%A9decins%20Sans%20Fronti%C3%A8res%20(MSF)%20to%20implore%20you%20to%20do%20everything%20within%20your%20power%20to%20ensure%20an%20immediate%20and%20sustained%20ceasefire%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip.%20You%20must%20demand%20that%20the%20Israeli%20government%20stop%20the%20deadly%20attacks%20on%20Palestinian%20civilians%20and%20allow%20crucial%20humanitarian%20aid%20to%20enter%20Gaza.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EToday%20across%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMSF%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40MSF%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20we%20begin%20a%20campaign%20for%20an%20immediate%20ceasefire%20%26amp%3B%20an%20end%20to%20the%20indiscriminate%20attacks%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FGaza%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23Gaza%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20simply%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FMustStopNow%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23MustStopNow%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20letter%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FUN%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40UN%3C%2Fa%3E%20Security%20Council%20demanding%20a%20stop%20to%20the%20deadly%20attacks%20on%20Palestinian%20civilians%F0%9F%91%87%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FQTs9zgD3EO%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FQTs9zgD3EO%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Christos%20Christou%20(%40DrChristou)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDrChristou%2Fstatus%2F1731684467046015299%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%204%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20noted%20that%20just%20like%20people%20across%20the%20world%2C%20the%20October%207%20attack%20by%20Hamas%20on%20Israeli%20civilians%20had%20been%20distressing%20and%20shocking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNow%2C%20after%2058%20days%2C%20words%20fail%20us%20to%20describe%20the%20absolute%20horror%20being%20inflicted%20on%20Palestinian%20civilians%20by%20Israel%20as%20it%20carries%20out%20incessant%20and%20indiscriminate%20warfare%20in%20Gaza%20for%20all%20the%20world%20to%20see%2C%E2%80%9D%20wrote%20the%20MSF%20chief.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20noted%20that%20before%20the%20truce%2C%20the%20MSF%E2%80%99s%20emergency%20team%20in%20Khan%20Younis%20had%20reported%20massive%20influxes%20of%20wounded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20strikes%20are%20also%20hitting%20overcrowded%2C%20squalid%20refugee%20camps%2C%20where%20people%20are%20barely%20surviving%20on%20the%20sparse%20humanitarian%20aid%20available.%20If%20the%20bombs%20do%20not%20get%20them%2C%20infectious%20diseases%20and%20starvation%20will.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStating%20that%20a%20sustained%20ceasefire%20was%20the%20only%20way%20to%20stop%20the%20killing%20of%20civilians%2C%20MSF%20also%20called%20for%20the%20establishment%20of%20an%20independent%20mechanism%20to%20oversee%20the%20flow%20of%20humanitarian%20supplies%20to%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFurthermore%2C%20we%20call%20for%20the%20implementation%20of%20secure%20and%20long-lasting%20medical%20evacuation%20routes%20to%20third%20countries%20for%20people%20suffering%20from%20severe%20injuries.%20In%20the%20short-term%2C%20the%20evacuation%20of%20these%20patients%20to%20Egypt%20through%20the%20Rafah%20crossing%20could%20be%20an%20option%2C%20and%20MSF%20is%20willing%20to%20contribute%20to%20scaling%20up%20necessary%20medical%20capacities%2C%E2%80%9D%20wrote%20the%20MSF%20chief.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20accused%20Israel%20of%20showing%20%E2%80%9Cblatant%20and%20total%20disregard%20for%20the%20protection%20of%20Gaza%E2%80%99s%20medical%20facilities%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20watching%20as%20hospitals%20are%20turned%20into%20morgues%20and%20ruins.%20These%20supposedly%20protected%20facilities%20are%20being%20bombed%2C%20are%20being%20shot%20at%20by%20tanks%20and%20guns%2C%20encircled%20and%20raided%2C%20killing%20patients%20and%20medical%20staff%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENoting%20that%20subjecting%20an%20entire%20population%20is%20a%20%E2%80%9Cwar%20crime%E2%80%9D%20under%20international%20humanitarian%20law%2C%20he%20wrote%20that%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20war%20was%20being%20%E2%80%9Cwaged%20on%20all%20of%20Gaza%20and%20its%20people%20at%20any%20cost%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MSF%20international%20president%20accused%20world%20leaders%2C%20including%20the%20permanent%20members%20of%20the%20UNSC%2C%20of%20being%20%E2%80%9Ccomplicit%E2%80%9D%20by%20%E2%80%9Cproviding%20Israel%20with%20diplomatic%20cover%2C%20by%20supplying%20Israel%20with%20seemingly%20unconditional%20military%20assistance%2C%20or%20by%20failing%20to%20help%20stem%20the%20relentless%20bloodshed%20and%20atrocities%20being%20committed%20in%20Gaza%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20time%20to%20choose%20whether%20the%20Council%20will%20continue%20issuing%20half-hearted%20calls%20for%20the%20respect%20of%20international%20law%20and%20the%20protection%20of%20civilians%2C%20or%20will%20fulfill%20its%20international%20peace%20and%20security%20mandate%20and%20exercise%20its%20full%20diplomatic%20leverage%20to%20convince%20the%20State%20of%20Israel%20that%20the%20death%20sentence%20it%20has%20handed%20the%20people%20of%20Gaza%20is%20inhumane%2C%20indefensible%2C%20and%20cannot%20continue%20to%20be%20carried%20out%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote%2C%20in%20the%20strongly-worded%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701709749000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F07173950%2Fimage1170x530cropped-2.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2