0Modi%E2%80%9D%20echoing%20in%20the%20chamber%20of%20the%20new%20parliament%20building.%20Protests%20that%20such%20enthusiasm%20was%20best%20reserved%20for%20a%20party%20office%20drowned%20in%20the%20loud%20cheers%20and%20slogans%20of%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EModi%20ki%20sarkar%2C%20teesri%20baar%20%3C%2Fem%3E(Modi%E2%80%99s%20government%20poised%20for%20a%20third%20term)%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%20Along%20with%20home%20minister%20Amit%20shah%20and%20defence%20minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%2C%20Modi%20watched%20the%20praise%20being%20showered%20silently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20elephant%20in%20the%20room%20was%20the%20Ethics%20Committee%20report%20that%20was%20listed%20to%20be%20tabled%20Monday%20but%20never%20was%20because%20the%20Treasury%20Benches%20were%20in%20no%20mood%20to%20allow%20Trinamool%20Congress%20(TMC)%20to%20steal%20its%20thunder.%20TMC%20members%2C%20who%20had%20a%20%E2%80%9Clukewarm%20response%E2%80%9D%20to%20Mahua%20Moitra%20till%20recently%2C%20rallied%20behind%20her%20with%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20adjourning%20twice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Lok%20Sabha%20Ethics%20Committee%20report%20has%20recommended%20the%20expulsion%20of%20Moitra%20over%20the%20%E2%80%9Ccash-for-query%E2%80%9D%20allegations%20levelled%20against%20her%20by%20BJP%20MP%20Nishikant%20Dubey.%20Moitra%20told%20reporters%20she%20will%20comment%20once%20the%20report%20is%20tabled.%20Mamata%20Banerjee%2C%20her%20party%20chief%2C%20had%20in%20a%20nod%20of%20support%20broken%20her%20silence%20on%20the%20controversy%20recently.%20Meanwhile%2C%20Dubey%20has%20accused%20the%20Leader%20of%20Opposition%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20TMC%20%3Cem%3Ebete%20noire%3C%2Fem%3E%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%20of%20leaking%20the%20Ethics%20panel%20report%2C%20while%20Choudhury%20had%20written%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20Speaker%20that%20expulsion%20is%20too%20harsh%20a%20punishment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20a%20reprieve%20for%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Raghav%20Chadha%20whose%20suspension%20was%20reversed%20by%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.%20Chadha%20apologised%20unconditionally%20and%20a%20motion%20was%20moved%20by%20BJP%20MP%20G.V.L.%20Narasimha%20Rao%20to%20revoke%20the%20suspension.%20Within%20a%20minute%20of%20his%20entry%20into%20the%20House%2C%20Chadha%20issued%20a%20video%20thanking%20Chairman%20Jagdeep%20Dhankar.%20%E2%80%9CAt%20least%20for%20115%20days%2C%20I%20was%20suspended.%20During%20those%20days%2C%20I%20could%20not%20ask%20your%20questions%20inside%20Parliament%20and%20was%20not%20able%20to%20raise%20your%20voice%20inside%20the%20House%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20happy%20that%20my%20suspension%20was%20ended.%20I%20am%20thankful%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20Rajya%20Sabha%20chairman%20for%20this%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChadha%20was%20suspended%20from%20the%20House%20in%20August%20for%20breach%20of%20privilege%20of%20the%20House.%20Four%20MPs%20had%20complained%20about%20the%20breach%20of%20their%20privilege%20stating%20that%20their%20names%20had%20been%20included%20in%20an%20amendment%20moved%20by%20Chadha%20to%20refer%20the%20Government%20of%20National%20Capital%20Territory%20of%20Delhi%20(Amendment)%20Bill%2C%202023%20to%20a%20Select%20Committee%20without%20their%20consent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Post%20Office%20Bill%202023%20was%20passed%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20and%20the%20Advocates%20(Amendment)%20Bill%2C%202023%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20on%20Monday%20before%20both%20Houses%20were%20adjourned%20to%20meet%20tomorrow.%20While%20the%20Advocates%20Bill%20seeks%20to%20get%20rid%20of%20touts%20in%20the%20various%20courts%2C%20it%20is%20the%20Postal%20Bill%20that%20will%20be%20viewed%20with%20concern.%20According%20to%20the%20proposed%20legislation%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20central%20government%20may%2C%20by%20notification%2C%20empower%20any%20officer%20to%20intercept%2C%20open%20or%20detain%20any%20item%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20the%20security%20of%20the%20State%2C%20friendly%20relations%20with%20foreign%20states%2C%20public%20order%2C%20emergency%20or%20public%20safety%2C%20or%20upon%20the%20occurrence%20of%20any%20contravention%20of%20any%20of%20the%20provisions%20of%20any%20law%20for%20the%20time%20being%20in%20force.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98This%20is%20an%20act%20of%20surveillance%20on%20citizens%2C%20fails%20to%20specify%20procedures%20and%20the%20grounds%20are%20very%20vague.%20Moreover%2C%20there%20are%20no%20consequences%20for%20the%20unauthorised%20opening%20of%20postal%20articles%20by%20a%20postal%20officer.%20This%20is%20a%20violation%20of%20articles%2019%20and%2021%20of%20the%20Indian%20Constitution%2C%E2%80%9D%20Congress%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Shaktisinh%20Govil%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20has%20demanded%2C%20during%20the%20session%2C%20a%20discussion%20on%20the%20Manipur%20violence%2C%20the%20Silkyara%20tunnel%20imbroglio%2C%20and%20the%20Indians%20on%20death%20row%20in%20Qatar.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701708459000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28190125%2FScreenshot-2023-07-28-at-6.59.30-PM_cleanup-1.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwinter-session-of-parliament-kicks-off-on-adjournment-note-two-bills-passed%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Though%20slated%20for%20the%20first%20day%20of%20this%20session%2C%20the%20Ethics%20Committee%20Report%20on%20Mahua%20Moitra%2C%20recommending%20her%20expulsion%20from%20parliament%2C%20was%20not%20tabled%20on%20Monday%2C%20December%204.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwinter-session-of-parliament-kicks-off-on-adjournment-note-two-bills-passed%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sandeep%20told%20Animal%20story%20only%20to%20Ranbir%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701708041000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105734543%2Cimgsize-19096.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fdid-you-know-sandeep-reddy-vanga-told-the-complete-story-of-animal-only-to-ranbir-kapoor%2Farticleshow%2F105734543.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F105734543.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ESandeep%20Reddy%20Vanga's%20'Animal'%2C%20starring%20Ranbir%20Kapoor%2C%20is%20receiving%20positive%20reviews.%20Siddhant%20Karnick%2C%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20Filmy%2C%20praised%20Ranbir's%20professionalism%20and%20mentioned%20the%20intense%20shoot%20in%20a%20glass%20house%20at%20Pataudi%20Palace.%20Ranbir%20remained%20dedicated%2C%20providing%20cues%20and%20accurately%20capturing%20reactions.%20Karnick%20also%20commended%20Anil%20Kapoor's%20enthusiasm%20during%20reading%20sessions%2C%20contributing%20to%20a%20strong%20working%20relationship.%20Only%20Ranbir%20knew%20the%20complete%20story%20shared%20by%20Vanga%2C%20bringing%20understanding%20to%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20team.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fdid-you-know-sandeep-reddy-vanga-told-the-complete-story-of-animal-only-to-ranbir-kapoor%2Farticleshow%2F105734543.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Byju's%20In%20Process%20To%20Raise%20Rs%20700%20Crore%20To%20Fund%20Operations%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EEdtech%20major%20Byju's%20is%20in%20process%20to%20raise%20Rs%20600-700%20crore%20to%20fund%20the%20company's%20operations%20till%20March%20by%20when%20it%20expects%20to%20realise%20money%20through%20the%20sale%20of%20Epic%20and%20partial%20stake%20sale%20in%20other%20subsidiaries%2C%20according%20to%20sources%20aware%20of%20the%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EByju's%20founder%20Byju%20Raveendran%20has%20recently%20raised%20money%20by%20mortgaging%20home%20and%20real%20estate%20assets%20owned%20by%20family%20members%20for%20paying%20salaries%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20about%20Rs%2050%20crore%20gap%20per%20month%20in%20operational%20expenses%20where%20a%20large%20component%20is%20salary.%20Promoters%20have%20pledged%20shares%2C%20home%2C%20and%20some%20other%20real%20estate%20assets%20of%20family%20members%20to%20bridge%20the%20gap%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20source%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPromoters%20are%20also%20in%20the%20process%20of%20raising%20debt%20of%20Rs%20600-700%20crore%20to%20help%20operations%20till%20March.%20By%20March%2C%20the%20situation%20will%20ease%20with%20the%20sale%20of%20Epic%20and%20partial%20stake%20sale%20in%20some%20other%20subsidiaries%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20source%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20source%20said%20Byju's%20has%20called%20an%20Annual%20General%20Meeting%20(AGM)%20on%20December%2020%20where%20the%20assets%20that%20have%20been%20pledged%20by%20the%20promoters%20will%20be%20brought%20to%20the%20notice%20of%20the%20company's%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20company%20is%20also%20in%20the%20process%20to%20submit%20a%20repayment%20schedule%20to%20the%20BCCI%20(Board%20of%20Control%20for%20Cricket%20in%20India)%20for%20Rs%20160%20crore%20sponsorship%20dues.%20Besides%20the%20sale%20of%20Epic%2C%20which%20is%20in%20advanced%20stages%2C%20existing%20investors%20are%20also%20expected%20to%20infuse%20funds%20into%20the%20company%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20source%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20AGM%20notice%20sent%20to%20shareholders%2C%20the%20company%20will%20also%20seek%20shareholders'%20approval%20for%20standalone%20and%20consolidated%20financial%20results%20for%20FY22.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20email%20query%20sent%20to%20Byju's%20elicited%20no%20reply.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20Manipal%20Education%20and%20Medical%20Group%20Chairman%20Ranjan%20Pai%20acquired%20a%20Rs%201%2C400%20crore%20debt%20raised%20by%20edtech%20major%20Byju's%20from%20Davidson%20Kempner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20settlement%20includes%20a%20penal%20amount%20claimed%20by%20Kempner%20against%20debt%20investment%20of%20USD%20100%20million%2C%20or%20about%20Rs%20800%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERanjan%20Pai%20is%20also%20in%20discussions%20to%20buy%20additional%20stakes%20in%20AESL%20shortly.%20Ranjan%20Pai's%20proprietary%20fund%2C%20Aarin%20Capital%2C%20was%20the%20first%20institutional%20investor%20in%20Byju's%20in%202013.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701707940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fs0a6d6rc_byju-raveendran-getty_625x300_30_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbyjus-in-process-to-raise-rs-700-crore-to-fund-operations-report-4633856%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Edtech%20major%20Byju's%20is%20in%20process%20to%20raise%20Rs%20600-700%20crore%20to%20fund%20the%20company's%20operations%20till%20March%20by%20when%20it%20expects%20to%20realise%20money%20through%20the%20sale%20of%20Epic%20and%20partial%20stake%20sale%20in%20other%20subsidiaries%2C%20according%20to%20sources.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbyjus-in-process-to-raise-rs-700-crore-to-fund-operations-report-4633856%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbyjus-in-process-to-raise-rs-700-crore-to-fund-operations-report-4633856%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbyjus-in-process-to-raise-rs-700-crore-to-fund-operations-report-4633856%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2211%20times%20Triptii%20sent%20internet%20into%20meltdown%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701707400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105734139%2Cimgsize-85016.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fweb-stories%2F11-times-triptii-dimri-sent-internet-into-meltdown%2Fphotostory%2F105734139.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F105734139.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E11%20times%20Triptii%20Dimri%20sent%20internet%20into%20meltdown%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fweb-stories%2F11-times-triptii-dimri-sent-internet-into-meltdown%2Fphotostory%2F105734139.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20State%20Polls%20Show%20No%20Real%20Challenge%20To%20Modi%20Before%202024%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMonths%20before%20the%20announcement%20of%20national%20elections%2C%20the%20close%20of%20year%202023%20couldn't%20have%20been%20better%20for%20the%20BJP%2C%20with%20its%20thumping%20victory%20in%20the%20Hindi%20heartland%20states%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Rajasthan%20and%20Chhattisgarh%20and%20its%20improved%20tally%20and%20vote%20share%20in%20the%20southern%20state%20of%20Telangana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20at%20all%20there%20was%20anything%20more%20to%20energise%20party%20workers%20and%20sympathisers%20with%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20arrived%20at%20the%20BJP%20headquarters%20at%20Deen%20Dayal%20Upadhyaya%20Marg%20in%20Delhi%2C%20a%20road%20named%20after%20the%20organisation's%20foremost%20ideologue%2C%20and%20declared%2C%20%26quot%3Ba%20hat-trick%20of%20wins%20is%20a%20guarantee%20of%20a%20hat-trick%20in%202024%20polls%26quot%3B.%20Behind%20him%2C%20a%20new%20banner%20said%20-%20%3Cem%3E%26quot%3BSapne%20nahin%2C%20haqeeqat%20bunte%20hain%3B%20tabhi%20toh%20sab%20Modi%20ko%20chahte%20hain%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Not%20just%20dreams%2C%20he%20shapes%20reality.%20That%20is%20why%20everyone%20wants%20Modi)%26quot%3B.%20A%20big%20message%20conveyed%20in%20simple%20words%2C%20easy%20to%20understand%20in%20almost%20any%20part%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGuarantee%26quot%3B%20is%20the%20new%20buzzword%20in%20politics.%20It%20was%20not%20original%20BJP%20coinage%20but%20lately%2C%20when%20the%20Congress%20and%20a%20few%20other%20opposition%20parties%20started%20using%20it%20full%20throttle%20to%20announce%20pre-poll%20freebies%2C%20Modi%20adapted%20it%20and%20added%20his%20punch%20-%20%3Cem%3E%26quot%3BModi%20ki%20guarantee%20ka%20matlab%20guarantee%20poora%20hone%20ki%20guarantee%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Modi's%20guarantee%20means%20the%20guarantee%20is%20guaranteed)%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20July%2C%20hours%20after%20the%20Congress%20and%20its%20allies%20moved%20a%20no-confidence%20motion%20against%20his%20government%20in%20parliament%2C%20Modi%20had%20%26quot%3Bguaranteed%26quot%3B%20that%20in%20his%20third%20term%2C%20India%20would%20become%20the%20biggest%20economy%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20election%20results%20for%20four%20states%2C%20announced%20on%20Sunday%2C%20suggests%20that%20voters%20in%20those%20states%20believed%20in%20him%20and%20his%20guarantees.%20The%20BJP%20had%20projected%20Modi's%20name%20and%20face%20for%20the%20governance%20model%20that%20it%20would%20provide%20in%20each%20of%20these%20states%20for%20the%20next%20five%20years.%20The%20results%20also%20indicated%20that%20Modi's%20personal%20charisma%20and%20goodwill%20remained%20intact%20or%20even%20somewhat%20enhanced%20in%20nearly%20a%20decade%20in%20power.%20This%20is%20based%20on%20his%20sincerity%2C%20strong%20political%20will%2C%20clear%20vision%20for%20policies%20and%20fair%20and%20transparent%20last%20mile%20delivery%20on%20the%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20after%20attending%20the%20opening%20day%20of%20the%20winter%20session%20of%20parliament%20he%20was%20off%20to%20Maharashtra%20for%20two%20events%20-%20to%20unveil%20a%20statue%20of%20Chhatrapati%20Shivaji%20Maharaj%20at%20Rajkot%20Fort%20in%20Sindhuburg%20and%20to%20attend%20the%20Navy%20Day%20celebrations.%20The%20political%2C%20social%20and%20security%20significance%20of%20the%20trip%20can%20be%20easily%20comprehended.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20massive%20victories%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Rajasthan%20and%20Chhattisgarh%20were%20even%20sweeter%20because%20nobody%20was%20giving%20the%20BJP%20a%203-0%20possibility%2C%20no%20opinion%20poll%2C%20no%20exit%20poll%2C%20no%20media%20reportage.%20The%20Congress%20and%20its%20'echo%20system'%20had%20created%20such%20hype%20that%20some%20predicted%20just%20the%20opposite%20-%20that%20the%20Congress%20would%20beat%20the%20BJP%203%3A1.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20do%20these%20results%20tell%20us%20in%20terms%20of%20messaging%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20that%20there%20is%20no%20real%20challenge%20to%20Modi%20and%20the%20BJP%20in%202024.%20Modi%20is%20likely%20to%20return%20to%20power%20for%20a%20third%20consecutive%20term.%20In%20the%20four%20states%20where%20results%20were%20announced%20Sunday%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%2065%20of%20the%20total%2082%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats.%20Telangana%20saw%20a%20triangular%20fight%20and%20out%20of%2017%20seats%2C%20the%20BJP%20won%20four.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20the%20BJP%20and%20Congress%20had%20direct%20face-offs%20in%20186%20seats.%20The%20BJP%20won%20170%2C%20which%20amounts%20to%20a%20bit%20over%2090%20per%20cent%20strike%20rate.%20In%202014%2C%20the%20BJP%20had%20won%20162%20of%20these%20seats%2C%20with%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20about%2085%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecond%2C%20abusive%20words%20and%20language%20used%20against%20PM%20Modi%20is%20counter-productive%20and%20backfires%20on%20those%20who%20use%20it.%20The%20Congress%20has%20clearly%20not%20learnt%20its%20lessons%20since%20Sonia%20Gandhi's%3Cem%3E%20%26quot%3BMaut%20Ka%20Saudagar%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%20remarks%20against%20Modi%20in%20the%20Gujarat%20election%20campaign%20in%202007.%20In%20these%20elections%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20called%20him%20%3Cem%3E%26quot%3BPanauti%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0(misfortune)%20and%20%3Cem%3E%26quot%3BPocket-maar%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%20(pickpocket).%20The%20results%20are%20for%20everyone%20to%20see.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThird%2C%20the%20results%20pose%20a%20real%20challenge%20to%20the%20longevity%20of%20the%20opposition%20INDIA%20grouping.%20After%20winning%20Telangana%2C%20some%20Congress%20leaders%2C%20in%20their%20enthusiasm%2C%20went%20over%20the%20top%20to%20say%20that%20decimating%20a%20regional%20party%20was%20a%20huge%20achievement.%20It%20indeed%20was%2C%20but%20the%20fact%20is%20that%20the%20INDIA%20grouping%20is%20about%20recognising%20the%20importance%20of%20regional%20parties%20and%20forming%20alliances%20with%20them.%20It's%20also%20a%20fact%20that%20regional%20parties%20emerged%20and%20came%20to%20the%20fore%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20Congress.%20The%20Congress's%20assertions%20is%20bound%20to%20upset%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20results%2C%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20(TMC)%2C%20RJD%20(Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal)%2C%20Janata%20Dal%20United%20(JDU)%20and%20some%20others%20have%20made%20uncharitable%20remarks%20about%20the%20Congress's%20attitude.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFourth%2C%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20INDIA%20grouping%20lost%20the%20central%20and%20perhaps%20only%20poll%20agenda%2C%20the%20caste%20census.%20The%20results%20proved%20that%20the%20agenda%20had%20no%20takers%2C%20so%20much%20so%20that%20two%20OBC%20Chief%20Ministers%2C%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20and%20Bhupesh%20Baghel%2C%20were%20shown%20the%20door.%20For%20Nitish%20Kumar%2C%20who%20championed%20the%20caste%20survey%2C%20the%20chips%20are%20down%20in%20Bihar%20after%20the%20language%20he%20used%20for%20women%20and%20young%20men%20while%20releasing%20socio-economic%20data%20in%20the%20Bihar%20legislative%20assembly%20and%20council.%20There%20is%20much%20talk%20about%20Nitish%20Kumar's%20status%20in%20Bihar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%2C%20in%20its%20wisdom%2C%20called%20the%20INDIA%20meeting%20on%20December%206%2C%20the%20day%20the%20Babri%20mosque%20in%20Ayodhya%20was%20razed%20by%20Hindu%20activists.%20The%20Congress%2C%20as%20hosts%2C%20will%20ignite%20debate%20and%20attempt%20to%20play%20on%20grounds%20where%20the%20BJP%20is%20a%20master%20of%20the%20game.%20More%20so%2C%20as%20the%20Ram%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20is%20to%20be%20inaugurated%20by%20Modi%20on%20January%2022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFifth%2C%20the%20results%20have%20exposed%20that%20freebies%20don't%20always%20work.%20The%20announcement%20has%20to%20be%20accompanied%20by%20good%20governance%2C%20delivery%20on%20the%20ground%20and%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20it%20reaches%20last%20mile.%20Modi%20stands%20tall%20because%20of%20his%20credible%20track%20record%2C%20both%20as%20Gujarat%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20Prime%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20'Modi%20and%20Mahila'%20is%20the%20most%20potent%20combo%20for%20the%20BJP%2C%20something%20that%20the%20Congress%20and%20its%20alliance%20partners%20may%20find%20even%20harder%20to%20counter%20when%20the%20nation%20votes%20for%20a%20new%20government%20in%20next%20few%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Sanjay%20Singh%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist%20based%20in%20Delhi)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701707280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Faru5tr18_modi-ani_625x300_04_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fstate-polls-show-no-real-challenge-to-modi-before-2024-4633783%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20e