%9Cno%20science%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20prove%20it%20is%20necessary%20to%20phase%20out%20fossil%20fuels%20in%20order%20to%20limit%20global%20warming.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20factual%20and%20I%20respect%20the%20science%2C%20and%20there%20is%20no%20science%20out%20there%2C%20or%20no%20scenario%20out%20there%2C%20that%20says%20that%20the%20phase-out%20of%20fossil%20fuels%20is%20what%E2%80%99s%20going%20to%20achieve%201.5%20%5Bdegrees%5D%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20at%20an%20online%20conference%20on%20November%2021%2C%20calling%20such%20discussion%20%E2%80%9Calarmist%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAl-Jaber%20was%20referring%20to%20the%20agreement%20among%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20governments%20in%202015%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscience.thewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fclimate-change-glossary-every-term-you-need-to-understand-explained%2F%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98pursue%20efforts%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20limiting%20global%20warming%20to%201.5%20%C2%B0C.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20continued%3A%20%E2%80%9C1.5%20is%20my%20north%20star.%20A%20phase-down%20and%20a%20phase-out%20of%20fossil%20fuels%2C%20in%20my%20view%2C%20is%20inevitable%2C%20it%20is%20essential%3B%20but%20we%20need%20to%20be%20real%2C%20serious%2C%20pragmatic%20about%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fscience-environment-67143989%5C%22%3Ephase-down%20of%20fossil%20fuel%20use%3C%2Fa%3E%20refers%20to%20the%20gradual%20reduction%20in%20their%20use%20but%20not%20a%20complete%20stop%20to%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20al-Jaber%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fscience-environment-67612929%5C%22%3Ewho%20is%20trained%20as%20an%20engineer%20and%20economist%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9Cscience%20has%20been%20central%20to%20my%20own%20career%20progress%20and%20yes%2C%20I%20respect%20the%20science%20in%20everything%20I%20do%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20BBC%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20honestly%20think%20there%20is%20some%20confusion%20out%20there%2C%20and%20misrepresentation.%20I%20am%20quite%20surprised%20with%20the%20constant%20and%20repeated%20attempts%20to%20undermine%20the%20work%20of%20the%20COP28%20presidency%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20also%20said%20according%20to%20the%20broadcaster.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20global%20phase-out%20of%20coal%2C%20oil%20and%20gas%20is%20proving%20to%20be%20controversial%20at%20the%20Dubai%20climate%20talks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UAE%C2%A0and%20several%20other%20countries%20have%20tried%20to%20shift%20the%20discussion%20to%20emerging%20technologies%20such%20as%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fcan-untested-carbon-removal-technology-beccs-help-deliver-climate-goals%2Fa-61639540%5C%22%3ECO%3Csub%3E2%3C%2Fsub%3E%20storage%20or%20capture%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20arguing%20that%20fossil%20fuels%20can%20still%20play%20an%20important%20role%20in%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20energy%20mix.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20experts%20have%20said%20these%20technologies%20are%20very%20expensive%20and%20cannot%20yet%20be%20scaled%20up%20to%20counter%20global%20heating.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20science%20is%20clear.%20The%201.5%20degree%20target%20is%20only%20possible%20if%20we%20finally%20stop%20burning%20fossil%20fuels%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20UN%20Secretary-General%20Antonio%20Guterres%20at%20the%20start%20of%20COP28%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fdeveloping-nations-should-be-given-fair-share-of-global-carbon-budget-pm-modi-at-cop28%5C%22%3EDeveloping%20Nations%20Should%20Be%20Given%20Fair%20Share%20of%20Global%20Carbon%20Budget%3A%20PM%20Modi%20at%20COP28%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia%20does%20not%20sign%20declarations%20on%20renewable%20energy%20and%20health%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20100%20countries%20endorsed%20a%20pledge%20at%20the%20COP28%20meeting%20that%20was%20mainly%20about%20tripling%20renewable%20energy%20installed%20capacity%20by%202030.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20did%20not%20endorse%20this%20pledge%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fcoal-phase-out-in-cop28-pledge-india-refrains-from-endorsing-it-9053276%2F%5C%22%3Edue%20to%20references%20in%20it%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20%E2%80%98phase-out%E2%80%99%20of%20coal%20and%20to%20ending%20new%20investments%20in%20the%20coal%20sector%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fenergy.ec.europa.eu%2Fsystem%2Ffiles%2F2023-12%2FGlobal_Renewables_and_Energy_Efficiency_Pledge.pdf%5C%22%3Edraft%20of%20the%20pledge%3C%2Fa%3E%20says%20that%20the%20deployment%20of%20renewables%20this%20decade%20must%20be%20accompanied%20by%20the%20%E2%80%9Cphase%20down%20of%20unabated%20coal%20power%2C%20in%20particular%20ending%20the%20continued%20investment%20in%20unabated%20new%20coal-fired%20power%20plants%2C%20which%20is%20incompatible%20with%20efforts%20to%20limit%20warming%20to%201.5%C2%B0C.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20such%20goals%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fsci-tech%2Fenergy-and-environment%2Fcop28-climate-summit-india-will-not-be-bound-by-curbs-on-energy-use-environment-secretary%2Farticle67601493.ece%5C%22%3Erun%20contrary%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20long-standing%20position%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20it%20needs%20to%20rely%20on%20coal%20power%20%E2%80%93%20its%20largest%20source%20of%20energy%20%E2%80%93%20to%20increase%20the%20standards%20of%20living%20for%20its%20population%2C%C2%A0%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20also%20did%20not%20sign%20a%20declaration%20on%20the%20impact%20of%20climate%20change%20on%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficials%20said%20that%20one%20of%20points%20in%20the%20declaration%20relating%20to%20cooling%20in%20the%20health%20sector%20may%20not%20be%20achievable%20in%20India%20in%20the%20short%20term%2C%20the%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20need%20cold%20storages%20for%20storing%20vaccines%20and%20medicines%20and%20these%20are%20linked%20to%20making%20our%20healthcare%20systems%20resilient%2C%E2%80%9D%20secretary%20of%20the%20Union%20environment%20ministry%20Leena%20Nandan%20told%C2%A0%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20added%3A%20%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20suggestions%20that%20using%20these%20are%20contributing%20to%20climate%20emissions%20and%20that%20we%20must%20choose%20some%20fuels%20over%20the%20other%20are%20not%20acceptable.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWith%20inputs%20from%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fcop28-uae-president-we-very-much-believe-climate-science%2Fa-67624227%5C%22%3EDW%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701706380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F04204251%2FSultan.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fcop-28-president-respect-science-india-declarations%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India's%20lack%20of%20endorsement%20for%20two%20declarations%20were%20because%20of%20references%20to%20a%20%E2%80%98phase-out%E2%80%99%20of%20coal%20power%20and%20what%20officials%20said%20were%20targets%20that%20are%20unviable%20for%20India's%20health%20sector.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fcop-28-president-respect-science-india-declarations%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mukhtar%20Ansari's%20Family%20Moves%20SC%20for%20His%20Transfer%20from%20UP%20Jail%2C%20Cites%20'Immediate%20Threat'%20to%20His%20Life%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F04211237%2FEffect-11.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20family%20of%20jailed%20