thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F16144735%2FScreenshot-2023-04-16-at-12.02.58-PM-1024x576.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-648838%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22675%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAtiq%20and%20Ashraf%20Ahmed%20moments%20before%20they%20were%20killed.%20Photo%3A%20Screengrab%20from%20video%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20weeks%20before%20the%20brothers%20were%20murdered%20by%20three%20mysterious%20assailants%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20police%20%E2%80%93who%20despite%20being%20in%20the%20line%20of%20fire%20for%20reasons%20known%20to%20them%20did%20not%20shoot%20the%20culprits%20in%20self-defence%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20dismissed%20Atiq%E2%80%99s%20plea%20seeking%20protection%20during%20his%20custody%20with%20the%20UP%20police%20in%20the%20Umesh%20Pal%20murder%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUmesh%20Pal%20was%20a%20key%20witness%20in%20the%20murder%20case%20of%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20(BSP)%20MLA%20Raju%20Pal%2C%20in%20which%20the%20ex-MP%20and%20ex-MLA%20were%20accused.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20petition%2C%20Mukhtar%E2%80%99s%20son%2C%20Umar%2C%20accused%20the%20Adityanath%20government%20of%20taking%20an%20%E2%80%9Cinimical%20position%E2%80%9D%20against%20the%20former%20MLA%20and%20hatching%20a%20%E2%80%9Clarger%20conspiracy%E2%80%9D%20to%20eliminate%20him%20while%20he%20is%20in%20jail.%20The%20threat%20perception%20is%20based%20on%20%E2%80%9Creliable%20information%E2%80%9D%20Mukhtar%20has%20received%20that%20his%20life%20is%20in%20grave%20danger%20and%20that%20there%20%E2%80%9Cis%20a%20conspiracy%20afoot%20involving%20several%20actors%20within%20the%20state%20establishment%E2%80%9D%20to%20assassinate%20him%20in%20Banda%20jail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUmar%20provides%20a%20graphic%20depiction%20of%20the%20way%20Mukhtar%E2%80%99s%20family%20fears%20he%20might%20be%20murdered.%20The%20same%20modus%20operandi%20had%20been%20used%20to%20carry%20out%20killings%20in%20jail%20in%20several%20other%20cases%2C%20he%20said.%20The%20petitioner%20said%20that%20a%20number%20of%20persons%20accused%20in%20the%20murder%20of%20BJP%20MLA%20Krishnanand%20Rai%20in%202005%20%E2%80%93%20Mukhtar%20was%20convicted%20and%20sentenced%20to%2010%20years%20earlier%20this%20year%20in%20a%20related%20case%20%E2%80%93%20had%20been%20killed%20by%20the%20Special%20Task%20Force%20of%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20police%20in%20similar%20circumstances.%20Even%20though%20Mukhtar%20and%20other%20accused%20persons%20had%20been%20acquitted%20in%20the%20murder%20of%20Krishnanand%20Rai%2C%20they%20are%20still%20viewed%20as%20culprits%20and%20the%20BJP%20leaders%20in%20the%20state%20have%20time%20and%20again%20sworn%20vengeance%20against%20them%20from%20public%20platforms%2C%20said%20Umar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20convicted%20politician%E2%80%99s%20son%20said%20that%20out%20of%20the%20persons%20accused%20of%20murdering%20Rai%2C%20four%20had%20already%20been%20murdered.%20While%20Firdaus%20was%20gunned%20down%20by%20the%20STF%20in%202006%2C%20Prem%20Prakash%20Singh%20alias%20Munna%20Bajrangi%20was%20murdered%20in%20Baghpat%20jail%20in%202018%20by%20another%20convicted%20gangster%20Sunil%20Rathi.%20More%20than%20a%20week%20before%20his%20murder%20Bajrangi%E2%80%99s%20wife%20Seema%20Singh%20had%20in%20a%20press%20conference%20in%20Lucknow%20on%20June%2029%20that%20year%20alleged%20that%20the%20UP%20police%20along%20with%20some%20political%20leaders%20and%20officials%20were%20conspiring%20to%20get%20him%20eliminated%20outside%20the%20jail%20in%20a%20%E2%80%9Cfake%20encounter%E2%80%9D.%20Singh%20had%20also%20claimed%20that%20during%20his%20stay%20in%20Jhansi%20jail%2C%20there%20had%20been%20an%20attempt%20to%20poison%20her%20husband.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20aide%20of%20Mukhtar%2C%20Rakesh%20Pandey%20was%20shot%20dead%20by%20the%20police%20in%20an%20alleged%20%E2%80%9Cencounter%E2%80%9D%20in%20August%202020%20after%20the%20SUV%20he%20was%20purportedly%20travelling%20in%20along%20with%20four%20other%20persons%20crashed%20into%20a%20tree%20in%20the%20early%20hours%20of%20a%20Sunday%20morning.%20Pandey%E2%80%99s%20family%20had%20accused%20the%20police%20of%20picking%20him%20up%20from%20home%20in%20Lucknow%20and%20then%20killing%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20June%202023%2C%20Sanjeev%20Maheshwari%20alias%20Jeeva%2C%20an%20alleged%20associate%20of%20Mukhtar%2C%20was%20shot%20dead%20inside%20a%20courtroom%20in%20Lucknow%20while%20he%20was%20being%20produced%20before%20the%20court.%20Jeeva%20had%20also%20been%20accused%20in%20the%20murder%20of%20BJP%20leader%20Brahm%20Dutt%20Dwivedi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20petition%2C%20Mukhtar%E2%80%99s%20son%20also%20accused%20the%20state%20government%20of%20covering%20up%20the%20murder%20of%20one%20Meraj%2C%20who%20had%20been%20a%20co-accused%20of%20Mukhtar%20in%20a%20MCOCA%20case%2C%20in%20which%20both%20were%20acquitted.%20In%20May%202021%2C%20an%20inmate%20of%20the%20Chitrakoot%20jail%20Anshu%20Dikshit%20allegedly%20shot%20dead%20Mukim%20Kala%20and%20Meraj%20with%20a%20firearm%2C%20inside%20the%20prison.%20Dikshit%2C%20who%20was%20lodged%20in%20a%20high-security%20barrack%2C%20was%20later%20shot%20dead%20by%20police%20after%20he%20allegedly%20held%20hostage%20five%20other%20inmates%20and%20threatened%20to%20kill%20them%2C%20according%20to%20the%20official%20version.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20must%20be%20noted%20that%20when%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20was%20in%20power%20in%20UP%2C%20the%20BJP%20as%20an%20Opposition%20party%20had%20alleged%20that%20Hindus%20in%20Kairana%2C%20in%20western%20UP%2C%20were%20being%20forced%20to%20leave%20their%20homes%20due%20to%20the%20fear%20of%20and%20intimidation%20by%20Mukim%20Kala%E2%80%99s%20alleged%20gang.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%202021%2C%20Mukim%20Kala%E2%80%99s%20mother%20had%20approached%20the%20Allahabad%20high%20court%20seeking%20protection%20for%20him%20when%20he%20had%20been%20detained%20in%20Saharanpur%20jail.%20She%20alleged%20that%20the%20police%20were%20harassing%20Mukim%20by%20trying%20to%20put%20pressure%20on%20her%20to%20withdraw%20a%20complaint%20filed%20by%20her%20against%20the%20police%20after%20her%20younger%20son%20Wasim%20was%20killed%20in%20an%20alleged%20encounter%20in%202017.%20In%20March%202021%2C%20the%20HC%20noted%20that%20the%20response%20from%20the%20government%20did%20not%20show%20any%20harassment%20of%20her%20son%20but%20directed%20the%20state%20to%20see%20that%20no%20harm%20was%20caused%20to%20Kala%20and%20to%20conduct%20operations%20as%20per%20the%20jail%20manual.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPolitics%20of%20%E2%80%98murders%E2%80%99%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20public%20submissions%20by%20politicians%20and%20even%20accused%20criminals%20about%20threats%20to%20their%20lives%20are%20often%20taken%20with%20a%20pinch%20of%20salt%2C%20the%20frequency%20and%20brazenness%20of%20such%20murders%20over%20the%20past%20few%20years%20make%20it%20necessary%20to%20reproduce%20the%20details%20of%20the%20threat%20perceived%20by%20these%20individuals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F22160156%2FF88FtkFbAAAwMpn.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F22160156%2FF88FtkFbAAAwMpn.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F22160156%2FF88FtkFbAAAwMpn-300x129.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F22160156%2FF88FtkFbAAAwMpn-1024x439.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681280%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22515%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EUP%20chief%20minister%20Adityanath%20at%20the%20Police%20Smriti%20Diwas%20event%20in%20Lucknow%20on%20October%2021%2C%202023.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40myogiadityanath%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20petition%2C%20Umar%20Ansari%20noted%3A%20%E2%80%9CAs%20per%20the%20information%20received%20from%20reliable%20sources%20within%20the%20police%20establishment%2C%20the%20persons%20who%20have%20been%20hired%20to%20assassinate%20the%20Petitioner%E2%80%99s%20father%20shall%20be%20arrested%20by%20the%20police%20or%20summoned%20on%20remand%20in%20some%20petty%20crime%2C%20produced%20before%20the%20court%20and%20then%20remanded%20to%20judicial%20custody.%20Then%2C%20they%20shall%20be%20taken%20to%20Banda%20Jail%20where%20the%20Petitioner%E2%80%99s%20father%20is%20currently%20lodged.%20This%20shall%20give%20the%20said%20persons%20the%20desired%20proximity%20to%20the%20Petitioner%E2%80%99s%20father.%20Thereafter%2C%20these%20hired%20killers%20will%20be%20provided%20access%20to%20arms%20inside%20jail%20and%20an%20opportunity%20by%20way%20of%20a%20lapse%20in%20security%20systems%20that%20they%20can%20take%20advantage%20of%20through%20complicit%20jail%20officials.%20The%20standard%20mode%20of%20operation%20is%20to%20give%20the%20attack%20the%20color%20of%20a%20fight%20between%20the%20inmates%20in%20order%20to%20give%20the%20entire%20incident%20the%20misleading%20cover%20of%20a%20%E2%80%98gang-war%E2%80%99%20(sic).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fsince-adityanath-took-over-in-2017-up-police-have-killed-190-people-in-encounters%5C%22%3ESince%20Adityanath%20Took%20Over%20in%202017%2C%20UP%20Police%20Have%20Killed%20190%20People%20in%20%E2%80%98Encounters%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMukhtar%20faces%20more%20than%2060%20criminal%20cases%20and%20after%20the%20BJP%20came%20to%20power%2C%20he%20has%20been%20convicted%20in%20six%20cases.%20This%20included%20the%20life%20sentence%20awarded%20to%20him%20by%20a%20Varanasi%20court%20in%20June%20for%20the%20murder%20of%20Awadesh%20Rai%2C%20the%20brother%20of%20Congress%20state%20president%20Ajay%20Rai%2C%20and%20the%2010%20years%20imprisonment%20awarded%20to%20him%20for%20kidnapping%20a%20Vishwa%20Hindu%20Parishad%20leader%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20murder%20of%20Krishnanand%20Rai%20in%202005.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMukhtar%20was%20born%20in%20Ghazipur%20district%20in%20East%20UP%2C%20bordering%20Varanasi.%20His%20family%20was%20linked%20to%20the%20Congress%20and%20he%20grew%20up%20with%20a%20Communist%20legacy%20through%20his%20grandfather%20and%20father.%20In%20his%20political%20career%2C%20Mukhtar%20and%20his%20brother%20have%20been%20associated%20with%20both%20the%20SP%20and%20the%20BSP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEver%20since%20the%20BJP%20came%20to%20power%20in%20UP%2C%20the%20Adityanath%20government%20treated%20him%20as%20the%20mascot%20of%20criminal%20politics%20and%20went%20after%20him%20through%20criminal%20cases.%20However%2C%20this%20took%20a%20sharp%20turn%20in%20July%202020%20when%20the%20Adityanath%20government%20was%20pushed%20to%20the%20backfoot%20after%20the%20Bikru%20incident%20in%20Kanpur%20where%20eight%20policemen%20were%20shot%20dead%20by%20history-sheeter%20Vikash%20Dubey%20and%20his%20associates.%20Dubey%20and%20several%20of%20his%20men%20were%20later%20shot%20dead%20by%20police%20in%20alleged%20encounters%2C%20with%20unsettled%20questions%20being%20raised%20over%20their%20genuineness.%20In%20terms%20of%20electoral%20politics%2C%20this%20was%20also%20a%20crisis%20for%20the%20BJP%20government%20vis-%C3%A0-vis%20the%20influential%20Brahmin%20community.%C2%A0%20To%20placate%20them%20and%20divert%20attention%20from%20the%20Bikru%20massacre%2C%20the%20state%20government%20unleashed%20a%20wave%20of%20punitive%20measures%20against%20other%20controversial%20figures%20in%20state%20politics%2C%20most%20prominent%20among%20them%20Mukhtar%2C%20who%20by%20virtue%20of%20being%20a%20Muslim%2C%20fitted%20perfectly%20into%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20polarising%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A170170636700