pply-order-of-496-000-litres-123120401174_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fbcl-industries-bags-rs-339-cr-ethanol-supply-order-of-496-000-litres-123120401174_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20Congress%20Shuns%20Alliance%20In%20Heartland%3A%20Senior%20Leader%20Explains%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESenior%20Congress%20leader%20Manickam%20Tagore%20underscored%20the%20importance%20of%20alliances%20and%20said%20it%20is%20the%20state%20level%20leaders%20in%20the%20Hindi%20heartland%20who%20need%20to%20understand%20it.%20Speaking%20to%20NDTV%20a%20day%20after%20the%20party's%20crushing%20defeat%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Telangana%2C%20Mr%20Tagore%20addressed%20the%20tide%20of%20criticism%20coming%20the%20way%20of%20the%20Congress.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party's%20Central%20leaders%2C%20he%20said%2C%20understand%20the%20need%20for%20alliances.%20Now%20the%20state-level%20leaders%20%26quot%3Bneed%20to%20understand%20the%20value%20of%20alliances%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%20This%2C%20however%2C%20is%20because%20of%20the%20binary%20nature%20of%20politics%20in%20states%20like%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20or%20Rajasthan%2C%20he%20contended.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20tough%20for%20the%20Congress%20to%20understand%20the%20importance%20of%20alliances%20because%20in%20states%20like%20MP%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Rajasthan%20there%20is%20no%20alliance%20politics%2C%26quot%3B%20Manickam%20Tagore%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20situation%2C%20he%20added%2C%20is%20different%20in%20state%20like%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20Kerala%20and%20Maharashtra.%20%26quot%3BThere%20we%20know%20the%20importance%20of%20alliance%20politics.%20In%20other%20states%20it%20takes%20a%20lot%20of%20time%2C%20because%20we%20think%20we%20are%20sacrificing%20our%20seats...%20State%20level%20leaders%20need%20to%20understand%20the%20value%20of%20alliances%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3