the%20INDIA%20bloc%20for%20the%20state%20assembly%20elections%2C%20Mr%20Abdullah%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20NC%20will%20be%20standing%20on%20its%20own%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCongress%20has%20won%20Telangana.%20They%20would%20have%20won%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Chhattisgarh%20and%20Rajasthan%2C%26quot%3B%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20had%20said.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20votes%20were%20cut%20by%20INDIA%20parties.%20This%20is%20the%20truth.%20We%20had%20said%20suggested%20a%20seat-sharing%20arrangement.%20They%20lost%20because%20of%20division%20of%20votes%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20the%20state%20assembly%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20called%20an%20%26quot%3Binformal%26quot%3B%20meeting%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20on%20November%206.%20Ms%20Banerjee%20said%20she%20would%20skip%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701705420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fpmgpi9i4_manickam-tagore_625x300_04_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Felection-results-2023-on-congresss-election-gameplan-suggestions-from-partys-senior-leader-manickam-tagore-4633737%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Senior%20Congress%20leader%20Manickam%20Tagore%20underscored%20the%20importance%20of%20alliances%20and%20said%20it%20is%20the%20state%20level%20leaders%20in%20the%20Hindi%20heartland%20who%20need%20to%20understand%20it.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Felection-results-2023-on-congresss-election-gameplan-suggestions-from-partys-senior-leader-manickam-tagore-4633737%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Felection-results-2023-on-congresss-election-gameplan-suggestions-from-partys-senior-leader-manickam-tagore-4633737%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Felect