nt'.%20Vice%20Admiral%20SN%20Kohli%20(Later%20Admiral)%20was%20the%20Flag%20Officer%20C-in-C%20of%20the%20WNC%2C%20and%20orders%20were%20given%20to%20dispatch%20the%20Naval%20fleet%20in%20Mumbai%20and%20Okha.%20The%20plan%20was%20to%20bomb%20the%20Karachi%20port.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20'Karachi%20Strike%20Group'%20from%20the%2025th%20Missile%20Boat%20Squadron%2C%20also%20known%20as%20the%20'Killer%20Squadron'%2C%20consisted%20of%20two%20Petya-class%20ships%20-%20Katchal%20and%20Kiltan%20-%20and%20three%20missile%20boats%20-%20INS%20Nirghat%2C%20Nipat%2C%20and%20Veer.%20One%20missile%20boat%20was%20stationed%20at%20the%20Dwarka%20port%20to%20provide%20cover.%20The%20missile%20boats%20were%20armed%20with%20four%20Russian%20Styx%20Surface-to-Surface%20missiles%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECommander%20Babru%20Bhan%20Yadav%2C%20the%20Killer%20Squadron's%20commanding%20officer%2C%20was%20ordered%20to%20dispatch%20for%20an%20offensive%20on%20Karachi%20port.%20The%20plan%20was%20to%20attack%20Karachi%20port%20on%20December%203%2C%20but%20the%20air%20raids%20by%20Pakistan%20occurred%20in%20the%20evening%2C%20making%20it%20difficult%20to%20launch%20an%20operation%20on%20the%20same%20day%3B%20therefore%2C%20D-day%20was%20changed%20to%20December%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Petyas%20were%20tasked%20to%20accompany%20the%20missile%20boats%20with%20their%20suitable%20radar%2C%20provide%20better%20targets%2C%20and%20tow%20a%20boat%20in%20case%20of%20an%20emergency.%20Before%20the%20war%2C%20the%20Pakistan%20Navy%20created%20a%2075-mile%20(120%20km)%20demarcation%20line%20for%20all%20merchant%20ships%20bound%20for%20Karachi%20and%20ordered%20them%20not%20to%20operate%20in%20that%20zone%20between%20sunset%20and%20dawn%2C%20and%20any%20boat%20picked%20on%20radar%20would%20be%20a%20Pakistani%20boat%20on%20patrol.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20'Killer%20Squadron'%20strike%20group%20reached%20112%20km%20south%20of%20Karachi%2C%20a%20target%20was%20identified%20northwest%20at%20a%20range%20of%2070%20km%2C%20and%20another%20target%20was%20spotted%20by%20the%20radar%20almost%2068%20km%20northeast.%20The%20strike%20group%20identified%20them%20as%20warships%20and%20Styx%20missiles%2C%20with%20a%20range%20of%2075%20km%2C%20were%20prepared%20for%20launch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EINS%20Nirghat%20engaged%20with%20the%20target%20in%20the%20northwest%20and%20fired%20two%20Styx%20missiles.%20The%20Styx%20destroyed%20PNS%20Khaibar.%20INS%20Nipat%20fired%20two%20missiles%20and%20sank%20a%20merchant%20ship%2C%20MV%20Venus%20Challenger%2C%20which%20was%20reportedly%20loaded%20with%20arms%20for%20the%20Pakistani%20army.%20INS%20Veer%20destroyed%20PNS%20Muhafiz%2C%20a%20coastal%20minesweeper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20book%20Transition%20to%20Triumph%2C%20Vice%20Admiral%20GM%20Hiranandani%20gives%20an%20analyzed%20account%20of%20the%20operation.%20When%20the%20strike%20group%20started%20closing%20in%20towards%20Karachi%2C%20INS%20Nirghat's%20radar%20mistook%20anti-aircraft%20tracer%20shells%20fired%20as%20aircraft%2C%20which%20created%20confusion%20and%20fear%20of%20a%20Pakistani%20air%20raid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EKarachi%20Port%20On%20Fire%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECommander%20BB%20Yadav%20onboard%20INS%20Nipat%20fired%20his%20remaining%20Styx%20missiles%20on%20the%20Kemari%20oil%20refinery%20and%20set%20it%20on%20fire.%20The%20attack%20was%20successful%2C%20and%20no%20loss%20was%20reported.%20It%20was%20the%20finest%20hour%20in%20the%20history%20of%20the%20Indian%20Navy.%20Four%20days%20later%2C%20Operation%20Python%20was%20the%20last%20nail%20in%20the%20coffin.%20INS%20Vinash%2C%20Talwar%2C%20and%20Trishul%20sank%20PNS%20Dacca%2C%20damaged%20MV%20Harmattan%20and%20MV%20Gulf%2C%20and%20the%20Kemari%20oil%20refinery%20burnt%20for%20days.%20Pakistan%20Navy's%20presence%20on%20the%20western%20front%20was%20in%20ashes%2C%20and%20India%20had%20complete%20maritime%20dominance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20first%20time%2C%20anti-ship%20missiles%20were%20used%20in%20the%20region.%20Commander%20Babru%20Bhan%20Yadav%20was%20awarded%20the%20Maha%20Vir%20Chakra%20for%20his%20gallant%20action%2C%20and%20the%20Navy%20celebrates%20December%204%20as%20'Navy%20Day'%20to%20honour%20the%20battle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bombing%20of%20Karachi%20port%20and%20the%20oil%20refinery%20resulted%20in%20a%20loss%20of%20around%20%243%20billion%20to%20Pakistan%20and%20a%20massive%20shortage%20of%20oil%20for%20Pakistani%20aircraft.%20It%20also%20cut%20the%20Sea%20Lines%20of%20Communication%20(SLOC)%20between%20East%20and%20West%20Pakistan%20and%20blocked%20any%20supply%20of%20US%20weapons%20to%20Pakistan%20via%20Karachi.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701697800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fsath25g_operation-trident_625x300_04_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexplained-when-indian-navys-killer-squadron-set-karachi-port-on-fire-in-1971-navy-day-operation-trident-4633345%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20the%20inevitability%20of%20a%201971%20war%20between%20India%20and%20Pakistan%2C%20Chief%20of%20Army%20Staff%2C%20General%20Sam%20Manekshaw%2C%20gave%20Prime%20Minister%20Indira%20Gandhi%20a%20paper%20on%20which%20he%20wrote%20December%204%2C%20the%20date%20on%20which%20India%20will%20go%20to%20war%20with%20Pakistan.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexplained-when-indian-navys-killer-squadron-set-karachi-port-on-fire-in-1971-navy-day-operation-trident-4633345%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexplained-when-indian-navys-killer-squadron-set-karachi-port-on-fire-in-1971-navy-day-operation-trident-4633345%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexplained-when-indian-navys-killer-squadron-set-karachi-port-on-fire-in-1971-navy-day-operation-trident-463334