20extend%20the%20agreement.%20On%20December%201%2C%20the%20truce%20collapsed.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701695340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fresqt0ok_israel-hamas-attack-afp_625x300_01_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Feyewitness-reveals-horrific-details-of-sexual-violence-during-october-7-hamas-attack-4633184%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hamas%20has%20denied%20allegations%20of%20sexual%20violence%2C%20but%20Israeli%20Defence%20Forces%20(IDF)%20claim%20that%20captured%20operatives%20have%20said%20they%20were%20ordered%20to%20%26quot%3Bdirty%26quot%3B%20the%20women.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Feyewitness-reveals-horrific-details-of-sexual-violence-during-october-7-hamas-attack-4633184%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Feyewitness-reveals-horrific-details-of-sexual-violence-during-october-7-hamas-attack-4633184%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Feyewitness-reveals-horrific-details-of-sexual-violence-during-october-7-hamas-attack-4633184%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22COP28%3A%20Adani%20Green%20Energy%20to%20invest%20%2422%20billion%20toward%20India's%202030%20goal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701695266000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-12%2F04%2Ffull%2F1701695191-4516.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fcop28-adani-green-energy-to-invest-22-billion-toward-india-s-2030-goal-123120400915_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Electricity%20demand%20is%20growing%207%25%20annually%2C%20dwarfing%20expansion%20in%20other%20economies.%20This%20led%20the%20govt%20to%20mandate%20the%20addition%20of%20both%20renewable%20and%20thermal%20capacity%20to