highlighting%20the%20discrepancies%20in%20the%20Baba%20Raghav%20Das%20Hospital%20in%20Gorakhpur%20%E2%80%94%20appeared%20bemused%20by%20the%20FIR%20lodged%20on%20December%201%2C%202023%2C%20as%20the%20memoir%20written%20by%20him%20was%20published%20in%202021.%20He%20linked%20it%20to%20the%20presumed%20depiction%20of%20his%20own%20experience%20of%20August%202017%20in%20the%20recent%20blockbuster%20movie%20%3Cem%3EJawan%3C%2Fem%3E%20starring%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan.%20Many%20fans%2C%20and%20Khan%20himself%2C%20believe%20that%20a%20part%20of%20the%20film%20where%20a%20doctor%20(played%20by%20actor%20Sanya%20Malhotra)%20who%20was%20falsely%20blamed%20for%20the%20death%20of%20several%20children%20at%20a%20hospital%2C%20was%20loosely%20based%20on%20the%20Gorakhpur%20paediatrician%E2%80%99s%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20FIR%20seems%20to%20be%20an%20impact%20of%20the%20appreciative%20letter%20I%20wrote%20to%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan%20after%20the%20release%20of%20the%20movie%2C%20which%20was%20a%20big%20hit%2C%E2%80%9D%20Khan%2C%20who%20has%20relocated%20to%20a%20city%20in%20south%20India%20to%20escape%20state%20harassment%20in%20his%20native%20UP%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhan%E2%80%99s%20book%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Gorakhpur%20Hospital%20Tragedy%3A%20A%20Doctor%E2%80%99s%20Memoir%20of%20a%20Deadly%20Medical%20Crisis%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20is%20described%20as%20his%20first-hand%20chronicle%20of%20the%20events%20of%20the%20fateful%20night%20in%20August%202017%2C%20when%20several%20infants%20died%20in%20the%20BRD%20Hospital%20in%20Adityanath%E2%80%99s%20political%20turf%20allegedly%20due%20to%20lack%20of%20oxygen%20supply.%20It%20also%20documents%20the%20persecution%20he%20faced%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20the%20state%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20allegedly%20scapegoat%20him%20to%20divert%20attention%20from%20administrative%20negligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20FIR%20against%20him%20and%20four-five%20unidentified%20others%20was%20lodged%20in%20the%20Krishna%20Nagar%20police%20station%20in%20Lucknow%20on%20the%20complaint%20of%20a%20local%20resident%20Manish%20Shukla%2C%20who%20trades%20in%20flex%20painting.%20He%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20he%20was%20a%20social%20activist%20and%20claimed%20that%20he%20had%20no%20affiliation%20to%20any%20political%20party%2C%20even%20though%20the%20description%20in%20his%20police%20complaint%20was%20heavily%20tilted%20in%20favour%20of%20shielding%20the%20image%20of%20the%20state%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20police%20complaint%2C%20Shukla%20starts%20by%20describing%20how%20he%20overheard%20four-five%20unidentified%20persons%20in%20a%20market-place%20discussing%20bringing%20down%20the%20government%20and%20rioting.%20The%20men%2C%20of%20whom%20he%20has%20not%20provided%20any%20markers%2C%20talk%20about%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20book%20and%20of%20him%20%E2%80%9Csecretly%E2%80%9D%20distributing%20it%20in%20the%20state%20and%20collecting%20funds%20from%20his%20community%2C%20mentioned%20as%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Eapne%20log%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20(Muslims)%2C%20for%20a%20%E2%80%9Csecret%20plot%E2%80%9D.%20Though%20he%20does%20not%20explicitly%20mention%20Muslims%2C%20the%20import%20of%20the%20references%20are%20clear%20as%20Khan%20is%20a%20Muslim.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShukla%20claimed%20that%20the%20men%20were%20discussing%20that%20Khan%20was%20trying%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20as%20many%20people%20of%20his%20community%20with%20the%20book%20before%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20and%20was%20%E2%80%9Csecretly%20meeting%E2%80%9D%20people%20to%20publicise%20the%20book.%20%E2%80%9CUnder%20any%20cost%2C%20a%20pro-Hindu%20government%20should%20not%20come%20to%20power%20at%20the%20Centre%2C%20and%20the%20Yogi%20government%20should%20also%20be%20uprooted%2C%20even%20if%20it%20requires%20inciting%20riots%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shukla%20said%2C%20quoting%20the%20alleged%20conversation%20of%20the%20mystery%20co-accused.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDescribing%20his%20reaction%20to%20the%20alleged%20conversation%2C%20Shukla%20said%20he%20felt%20%E2%80%9CDr.%20Kafeel%E2%80%99s%20people%20can%20spread%20hate%20among%20the%20public%20at%20a%20large%20scale%20and%20disturb%20peace%3B%20they%20could%20also%20incite%20riots%20or%20even%20be%20terrorists.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShukla%20said%20he%20did%20not%20confront%20the%20men%20and%20decided%20to%20call%20his%20friends%20first.%20But%20when%20he%2C%20along%20with%20his%20friends%2C%20confronted%20the%20co-accused%2C%20they%20escaped%20in%20the%20dark%2C%20dropping%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20book%20written%20by%20Khan.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20did%20not%20run%20after%20them%20fearing%20that%20they%20might%20be%20carrying%20bombs%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shukla%20said%20in%20the%20FIR.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20complaint%2C%20Shukla%20said%20the%20book%20falsely%20held%20the%20Adityanath%20government%20responsible%20for%20the%20Gorakhpur%20oxygen%20tragedy.%20The%20book%20was%20written%20to%20%E2%80%9Cenrage%E2%80%9D%20a%20%E2%80%9Cspecific%20community%E2%80%9D%2C%20to%20spread%20riots%20and%20%E2%80%9Cclass%20hatred%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20depicts%20an%20%E2%80%9Cimaginary%20plight%E2%80%9D%20of%20UP%E2%80%99s%20health%20system%2C%20leading%20to%20fear%20among%20the%20people%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShukla%20also%20claimed%20that%20Khan%20penned%20the%20book%20based%20on%20%E2%80%9Cunverified%20material%20and%20forged%20documents%E2%80%9D%20to%20garner%20sympathy%20over%20the%20criminal%20cases%20he%20faces%20over%20the%20Gorakhpur%20incident%20as%20well%20as%20for%20protesting%20against%20the%20CAA-NRC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20FIR%20charges%20Khan%20and%20others%20under%20a%20dozen%20penal%20clauses%2C%20including%20Aections%20153A%20(promoting%20enmity%20between%20different%20groups)%2C%20295A%20(deliberate%20and%20malicious%20acts%20intended%20to%20outrage%20religious%20feelings)%2C%20465%20(forgery)%2C%20298%20(uttering%20words%20with%20deliberate%20intent%20to%20wound%20religious%20feelings)%20and%20504%20(intentional%20insult%20with%20intent%20to%20provoke%20breach%20of%20peace)%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code.%20The%20FIR%20also%20invokes%20Sections%203%20and%2012%20of%20the%20Press%20and%20Registration%20of%20Books%20Act%2C%201867.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhan%20said%20the%20charges%20against%20him%20in%20the%20FIR%2C%20based%20on%20the%20conversation%20of%20some%20unknown%20persons%20about%20him%20and%20his%20book%2C%20was%20absurd.%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EBewakoofi%20ki%20baatein%20hai%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0(This%20is%20stupid)%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CEveryone%20and%20anyone%20can%20buy%20and%20read%20my%20book.%20The%20kids%20who%20died%20in%20the%20Gorakhpur%20hospital%20were%20not%20from%20one%20community.%20They%20were%20all%20from%20poor%20families.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhan%20also%20found%20absurd%20the%20fact%20that%20though%20his%20book%2C%20which%20is%20today%20available%20in%20six%20languages%20(English%2C%20Urdu%2C%20Hindi%2C%20Malayalam%2C%20Tamil%20and%20Marathi)%2C%20was%20released%20in%202021%2C%20the%20police%20complaint%20against%20it%20was%20filed%20now.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20government%20has%20not%20banned%20the%20book%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Khan%20when%20asked%20to%20react%20to%20the%20various%20allegations%20levelled%20in%20the%20FIR%20over%20the%20motive%20of%20the%20memoir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20feels%20the%20FIR%20could%20be%20motivated%20by%20the%20publicity%20he%20garnered%20following%20the%20success%20of%20the%20movie%3Cem%3E%20Jawan%3C%2Fem%3E.%20In%20October%2C%20in%20a%20public%20letter%20to%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan%2C%20the%20doctor%20said%20the%20movie%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cpoignant%20portrayal%20of%20the%20tragic%20Gorakhpur%20Encephalitis%20incident%20has%20left%20an%20indelible%20mark%20on%20my%20heart%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhan%20wrote%3A%20%E2%80%9CAs%20someone%20who%20has%20had%20a%20personal%20connection%20with%20the%20incident%20and%20its%20aftermath%2C%20I%20was%20profoundly%20moved%20by%20your%20decision%20to%20bring%20this%20story%20to%20the%20screen.%20While%20I%20understand%20that%20%E2%80%98Jawan%E2%80%99%20is%20a%20work%20of%20fiction%2C%20the%20parallels%20it%20draws%20to%20the%20Gorakhpur%20tragedy%20serve%20as%20a%20powerful%20reminder%20of%20the%20systemic%20failures%2C%20apathy%2C%20and%2C%20most%20importantly%2C%20the%20innocent%20lives%20lost.%20It%20underscores%20the%20urgent%20need%20for%20accountability%20within%20our%20healthcare%20system.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhan%20also%20refers%20to%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20the%20character%20played%20by%20Sanya%20Malhotra%20encapsulates%20his%20own%20experience%20but%20also%20distinguishes%20between%20the%20attainment%20of%20justice%20on%20reel%20and%20in%20his%20real%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20heartening%20to%20witness%20the%20real%20culprit%20of%20%E2%80%98The%20Gorakhpur%20Hospital%20Tragedy%E2%80%99%20got%20caught%20%2C%20though%20sadly%20in%20real%20life%20the%20real%20culprits%20are%20roaming%20free%20%2C%20me%20still%20struggling%20to%20get%20my%20job%20back%20%2C%20and%20those%2063%20parents%20who%20lost%20their%20little%20ones%20still%20waiting%20for%20justice%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20being%20terminated%20from%20his%20services%20over%20the%20events%20following%20the%20Gorakhpur%20tragedy%20as%20a%20government%20doctor%20in%20BRD%20hospital%20in%20November%202021%2C%20Khan%20is%20still%20fighting%20a%20legal%20battle%20in%20the%20Allahabad%20high%20court%20to%20get%20his%20job%20restored.%20He%20was%20initially%20hailed%20as%20a%20hero%20by%20a%20section%20of%20media%20and%20civil%20society%20for%20trying%20to%20save%20the%20lives%20of%20many%20infants%20through%20his%20own%20resources%20during%20the%20oxygen%20shortage%20incident%20but%20was%20booked%20and%20arrested%20by%20the%20government%20for%20attempting%20to%20commit%20culpable%20homicide%20and%20other%20charges.%20In%20April%202018%2C%20while%20granting%20bail%20to%20him%20after%20he%20spent%20seven%20months%20in%20jail%2C%20the%20Allahabad%20high%20court%20said%20there%20was%20no%20%E2%80%9Cno%20material%20on%20record%2C%20which%20may%20establish%20medical%20negligence%20against%E2%80%9D%20him%20individually%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20death%20of%20infants%20in%20the%20Gorakhpur%20hospital%20in%20August%2C%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20an%20internal%20inquiry%20absolved%20Khan%20of%20the%20major%20charges%20against%20him%20in%20the%202017%20BRD%20hospital%20oxygen%20tragedy%2C%20but%20the%20government%20later%20said%20that%20he%20had%20not%20been%20given%20a%20clean%20chit%20yet%20and%20initiated%20a%20fresh%20inquiry%20against%20him%20for%20spreading%20%E2%80%9Cmisinformation%E2%80%9D%20about%20the%20probe%20report%20and%20for%20making%20%E2%80%9Canti-government%E2%80%9D%20political%20comments%20during%20the%20period%20of%20his%20suspension.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20September%202020%2C%20the%20Allahabad%20high%20court%20set%20aside%20the%20National%20Security%20Act%20order%20passed%20against%20him%20for%20allegedly%20making%20inflammatory%20and%20provocative%20comments%20in%20a%20speech%20against%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%20at%20the%20Aligarh%20Muslim%20University%20in%202019%20December.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20termed%20the%20NSA%20order%20illegal%20and%20directed%20the%20state%20government%20to%20forthwith%20release%20him%20from%20jail.%20Khan%20had%20been%20booked%20under%20the%20stringent%20law%20on%20the%20day%20he%20was%20expected%20to%20be%20released%20on%20bail%20from%20Mathura%20jail%20where%20he%20was%20lodged%20after%20his%20arrest%20in%20the%20case%20on%20January%2029%2C%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701691203000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F09%2F30141305%2Fkafeel-khan.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fup-police-files-fir-against-dr-kafeel-khan-for-instigating-minority-community-with-his-2021-memoi