communities%20constituted%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Felections%2Fstory%2Ftribal-vote-bjp-congress-election-jharkhand-madhya-pradesh-rajasthan-2462929-2023-11-15%5C%22%3Esignificant%20percentage%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20population%20in%20three%20%E2%80%93%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Rajasthan%20and%20Chhatisgarh%20%E2%80%93%20of%20the%20four%20states%20that%20went%20to%20the%20polls%20in%20November.%20Just%20under%20a%20third%20or%2031%25%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20tribal%20population%20is%20found%20in%20these%20three%20states.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fbjp-sweeps-tribal-seats-across-mp-chhattisgarh-bap-opens-account%2Farticle67602226.ece%2Famp%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20reports%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20won%20just%2019%20of%20the%2076%20seats%20reserved%20for%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20(ST)%20candidates%20in%20MP%20and%20Chhattisgarh%20in%202018%2C%20managed%20to%20bag%2044%20this%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChhattisgarh%2C%20created%20along%20with%20Jharkhand%20to%20give%20tribal%20communities%20more%20representation%2C%20has%2029%20seats%20reserved%20for%20ST%20candidates%20in%20the%2090-member%20assembly.%20According%20to%20the%20census%20conducted%20in%202011%2C%20tribals%20constitute%2030.60%25%20of%20Chhattisgarh%E2%80%99s%20population.%20In%202018%2C%20Congress%20won%20a%20majority%20of%20tribal%20seats%20in%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20leaving%20the%20BJP%20with%20only%20four.%20But%20this%20time%2C%20the%20BJP%20won%2017%20of%20the%2029%20seats.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202003%2C%20the%20BJP%20won%20as%20many%20as%2024%20of%20the%2033%20tribal%20seats%20in%20Chhatisgarh%2C%20with%20Congress%20winning%20nine.%20That%20was%20the%20new%20state%E2%80%99s%20first%20election%2C%20and%20after%20delimitation%2C%20the%20seats%20reserved%20for%20ST%20candidates%20shrank%20to%2029.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Adivasis%20and%20other%20tribal%20groups%20comprise%2021.1%25%20of%20the%20population.%20Of%20the%20230%20constituencies%2C%2047%20are%20reserved%20for%20ST%20candidates.%20In%202018%2C%20Congress%20won%2030%20of%20those%2047%20seats.%20This%20time%2C%20the%20dial%20flipped%20and%20the%20BJP%20won%2027.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20Rajasthan%2C%20ST%20communities%20constitute%2013.5%25%20of%20the%20state.%20In%202018%2C%20of%20the%2025%20seats%20reserved%20for%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20in%20the%20state%2C%20the%20Congress%20won%2012%20and%20the%20BJP%20nine.%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20reports%20that%20this%20time%20around%2C%20the%20BJP%20managed%20to%20add%20four%20more%20ST%20seats%20to%20its%20tally%20compared%20to%202018%2C%20%E2%80%9Ceven%20as%20new%20entrant%20Bharat%20Adivasi%20Party%20capitalised%20on%20changing%20ideas%20of%20tribal%20identity%20with%20its%20%E2%80%98alternate%20politics%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20leaders%20insisted%20won%20it%20three%20seats%20in%20Rajasthan%20(Dhariawad%2C%20Aspur%2C%20and%20Chorasi)%20and%20one%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20(Sailana).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20question%20of%20the%20RSS%E2%80%99s%20reference%20to%20tribals%20as%20%3Cem%3Evanvasi%3C%2Fem%3E%20(forest%20dwellers)%20and%20not%20Adivasi%20(original%20inhabitants)%20was%20made%20much%20of%20in%20Rahul%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20speeches%2C%20but%20the%20difference%20remained%20an%20important%20plank%20of%20the%20Sangh%20pitch%2C%20which%20dates%20back%20decades.%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20reports%20that%20in%20both%20the%20Surguja%20and%20Bastar%20belts%2C%20where%20most%20ST%20seats%20are%2C%20the%20%E2%80%9CCongress%20took%20a%20beating%20from%20the%20BJP%20%E2%80%93%20losing%20almost%20all%E2%80%9D.%20It%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20constituencies%20like%20Narayanpur%20(Bastar)%2C%20the%20Congress%20fell%20between%20two%20stools%2C%20as%20the%20Baghel%20administration%20took%20positions%20similar%20to%20that%20by%20the%20BJP%20before%2C%20alienating%20besieged%20%E2%80%98vishwasis%E2%80%99%20(believers).%20Christian%20tribals%20were%20upset%20with%20the%20Congress%20for%20not%20acting%20on%20rising%20attacks%20against%20them%20even%20as%20the%20BJP%20made%20it%20a%20point%20to%20mention%20religious%20conversion%20by%20missionaries%20as%20a%20campaign%20issue.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThen%2C%20as%20reported%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20their%20material%20needs%20could%20not%20be%20met%20as%20a%20priority%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fchhattisgarh-maoist-dantewada-development%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eas%20Chhannu%20Netam%2C%2025%2C%20told%20The%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CAdivasis%20have%20nothing%20here.%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20roads.%20There%20is%20a%20school%20in%20our%20village%20but%20till%2010th%20standard.%20We%20want%20roads%2C%20we%20want%20connections%20under%20Har%20Ghar%20Jal%20%5Bthe%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20flagship%20scheme%20to%20provide%20water%20pipe%20connections%20to%20every%20rural%20household%5D%2C%20we%20should%20get%20jobs.%20Bastar%E2%80%99s%20Adivasis%20are%20where%20they%20were.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESimilarly%2C%20the%20BJP%20added%20at%20least%2019%20ST%20seats%20to%20its%20tally%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20this%20election%2C%20with%20large%20swathes%20in%20the%20Mahakaushal%20and%20Malwa-Nimar%20regions%20%E2%80%93%20like%20Ghoradongri%2C%20Bhainsdehi%2C%20Mandla%2C%20Alirajpur%20%E2%80%93%20shifting%20from%20the%20Congress%20to%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20pitch%20this%20time%20for%20tribals%20has%20rested%20on%20the%20election%20of%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu%2C%20as%20well%20as%20offers%20for%20special%20benefits%20and%20%E2%80%9Ctribal%20culture%E2%80%9D.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Felections%2Fstory%2Ftribal-vote-bjp-congress-election-jharkhand-madhya-pradesh-rajasthan-2462929-2023-11-15%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3EIndia%20Today%3C%2Fem%3E%20writes%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9CBJP%20has%20been%20on%20an%20overdrive%20to%20secure%20the%20tribal%20votebank.%20From%20the%20Rani%20Durgavati%20Gaurav%20Yatra%20in%20June%20to%20pay%20homage%20to%20the%2016th%20century%20Gond%20queen%20Rani%20Durgavati%20to%20renaming%20a%20railway%20station%20in%20Indore%20after%20Tantya%20Bhil%2C%20a%20tribal%20icon%20from%20the%20Bhil%20community.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20Rajasthan%2C%20the%20new%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Findia%2Frajasthan-polls-bharat-adivasi-party-candidate-rajkumar-roat-wins-chorasi-seat%2Fcid%2F1984249%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EBharat%20Adivasi%20Party%20(BAP)%20candidate%20Rajkumar%20Roat%20won%20the%20Chorasi%20assembly%20constituency%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20This%20was%20one%20seat%2C%20but%20the%20failure%20to%20have%20an%20understanding%20or%20alliance%20with%20forces%20such%20as%20this%20in%20Rajasthan%20or%20in%20Chhatisgarh%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20with%20the%20Gondwana%20Ganatantra%20Party%20(GGP)%20may%20have%20given%20the%20Congress%20the%20illusion%20of%20allowing%20it%20to%20keep%20a%20significant%20base%20intact%2C%20but%20it%20enabled%20the%20BJP%20to%20pick%20up%20seats%20and%20as%20a%20result%2C%20build%20important%20talking%20points%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%202024%20elections.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ffailed-promises-and-tokenism-why-modis-renewed-tribal-push-doesnt-exude-confidence%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20last%20week%2C%20the%20BJP%20had%20left%20no%20stone%2