Israeli%20soldiers%20and%20settlers%20are%20quick%20to%20repress%20such%20efforts%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.972mag.com%2Fharun-abu-aram-masafer-yatta%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eviolently%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.972mag.com%2Fhaj-suleiman-masafer-yatta-police%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecracking%20down%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0on%20Palestinians%20trying%20to%20hold%20on%20to%20their%20land.%20In%20this%20context%2C%20the%20presence%20of%20non-Palestinian%E2%80%94and%20especially%20Israeli%20Jewish%E2%80%94activists%20becomes%20a%20useful%20avenue%20of%20resistance.%20Israelis%2C%20and%20to%20some%20extent%20foreign%20nationals%2C%20find%20it%20easier%20to%20engage%20in%20nonviolent%20direct%20action%20like%20filming%20settler%20and%20army%20transgressions%20because%20they%20enjoy%20significant%20protections%20under%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20civilian%20legal%20system%2C%20unlike%20Palestinians%E2%80%94who%2C%20if%20arrested%2C%20are%20tried%20in%20Israeli%20military%20courts%20and%20sentenced%20to%20harsh%20punishments%20with%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hrw.org%2Freport%2F2021%2F04%2F27%2Fthreshold-crossed%2Fisraeli-authorities-and-crimes-apartheid-and-persecution%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%2099%25%20rate%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0of%20conviction.%20By%20being%20present%20at%20the%20scene%2C%20such%20activists%20are%20thus%20freer%20to%20involve%20Israeli%20police%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20deter%20settlers%2C%20demand%20that%20soldiers%20show%20the%20orders%20they%20are%20following%20rather%20than%20acting%20arbitrarily%20or%20illegally%2C%20and%20sometimes%20even%20use%20their%20bodies%20to%20nonviolently%20obstruct%20house%20demolitions%2C%20evictions%2C%20arrests%2C%20and%20assaults%20targeting%20Palestinians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EWhile%20such%20activism%20has%20not%20been%20enough%20to%20halt%20the%20overall%20pace%20of%20the%20dispossession%2C%20it%20has%20nevertheless%20had%20some%20important%20successes.%20Large%20mobilisations%20of%20Palestinian%2C%20Israeli%2C%20and%20international%20activists%20have%20been%20able%20to%20delay%20or%20even%20avert%20destruction%20of%20entire%20villages%2C%20like%20in%20the%20case%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.972mag.com%2Fin-khan-al-ahmar-i-found-renewed-hope-for-resisting-the-occupation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKhan%20al-Ahmar%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0in%202018%2C%20where%20the%20Israeli%20government%20was%20forced%20to%20indefinitely%20delay%20the%20demolition%20of%20the%20village.%20%E2%80%9CEvery%20single%20day%20that%20we%20are%20able%20to%20help%20stop%20the%20Palestinian%20communities%20from%20getting%20displaced%20is%20a%20success%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Guy%20Hirschfeld%2C%20an%20Israeli%20activist%20from%20the%20group%20Looking%20the%20Occupation%20in%20the%20Eye.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fgaza-biden-ceasefire-pause%5C%22%3EWhen%20the%20Ceasefire%20Ends%2C%20Biden%20Shouldn%E2%80%99t%20Allow%20Israel%20to%20Continue%20Its%20Futile%20War%20of%20Reprisal%20in%20Gaza%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EFor%20years%2C%20such%20activism%20has%20also%20attempted%20to%20check%20the%20rising%20dispossession%20in%20smaller%20ways%2C%20especially%20through%20the%20use%20of%20filming.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20there%20is%20no%20documentation%2C%20then%20unfortunately%20it%E2%80%99s%20like%20the%20event%20didn%E2%80%99t%20happen%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Yeheli%20Cialic%20from%20Mesarvot%2C%20an%20anti-occupation%20group%20that%20supports%20Israeli%20military%20service%20refusers.%20Arik%20Asherman%2C%20who%20led%20the%20Israeli%20group%20Rabbis%20for%20Human%20Rights%20for%20two%20decades%2C%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9Cfilming%20settlers%20deters%20them%20a%20bit.%E2%80%9D%20Such%20recordings%20are%20also%20useful%20in%20protecting%20Palestinians%20and%20allies%20against%20false%20accusations%20of%20attacking%20settlers%20or%20soldiers.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20have%20been%20cases%20where%20the%20police%20or%20the%20army%20wanted%20to%20frame%20us%2C%20and%20the%20footage%20saved%20us%20because%20it%20showed%20that%20we%20didn%E2%80%99t%20do%20what%20the%20army%20accused%20us%20of%2C%E2%80%9D%20Asherman%20said.%20On%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fprogressive.org%2Flatest%2Fharassment-and-attacks-on-human-rights-activists-stein-20231002%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erare%20occasions%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20visual%20evidence%20has%20even%20helped%20compel%20the%20Israeli%20police%20to%20register%20a%20case%20against%20violent%20settlers.%20Filming%20has%20also%20made%20the%20occupation%20more%20visible%20to%20the%20international%20community%20and%20the%20Israeli%20public%2C%20with%20human%20rights%20organizations%20like%20B%E2%80%99Tselem%20including%20visual%20evidence%20of%20violence%20in%20their%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.btselem.org%2Fpublications%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereports%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.btselem.org%2Fvideo-channel%2Fall%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edatabases%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20journalists%20relying%20on%20the%20footage%20in%20their%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F11%2F02%2Fworld%2Fmiddleeast%2Fwest-bank-palestinians-israel-settlers.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereporting%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EEven%20before%20October%207%2C%20doing%20protective%20presence%20work%20was%20not%20easy.%20As%20Hirschfeld%20told%20me%2C%20activists%20%E2%80%9Care%20sometimes%20hated%20more%20than%20Palestinians%2C%E2%80%9D%20with%20settlers%20and%20soldiers%2C%20as%20well%20as%20Israeli%20media%2C%20seeing%20them%20as%20antisemites%2C%20traitors%2C%20and%20Hamas%20supporters.%20Still%2C%20activists%20were%20able%20to%20operate%20relatively%20safely%20most%20of%20the%20time.%20But%20amid%20the%20growing%20militarization%20of%20West%20Bank%20settlers%2C%20that%20safety%20has%20become%20increasingly%20precarious.%20According%20to%20%3Cem%3EHaaretz%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20Israeli%20army%20has%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.haaretz.com%2Fisrael-news%2F2023-11-02%2Fty-article%2F.premium%2Fisraels-army-to-recruit-settlers-with-no-army-experience-to-guard-west-bank-settlements%2F0000018b-8f63-d7a8-afcf-afe3a9b00000%3Flts%3D1701200679918%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edistributed%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%208%2C000%20weapons%20to%20settlement%20defense%20squads%20and%20regional%20battalions%20in%20the%20West%20Bank%20since%20October%207%2C%20and%20plans%20to%20recruit%20settlers%20with%20no%20prior%20military%20experience%20to%20%E2%80%9Cdefend%E2%80%9D%20the%20settlements.%20Activists%20on%20the%20ground%20are%20seeing%20the%20results%20of%20that%20policy.%20%E2%80%9CA%20lot%20of%20settlers%20are%20enlisted%20into%20some%20settlement%20security%20force.%20Some%20are%20in%20uniform%2C%20some%20not%2C%20and%20all%20have%20military-grade%20weapons%2C%E2%80%9D%20Vardi%20told%20me.%20Eisner%20agreed%20that%20there%20has%20been%20a%20%E2%80%9Cproliferation%20of%20weaponry%20in%20settlements%20under%20the%20guise%20of%20security%2C%E2%80%9D%20noting%20that%20%E2%80%9Csettlers%20see%20themselves%20as%20part%20of%20the%20Israeli%20war%20effort.%E2%80%9D%20In%20addition%20to%20being%20armed%20and%20given%20free%20rein%2C%20Vardi%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9Csettlers%20are%20talking%20about%20revenge%E2%80%94and%20they%20mean%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F14161537%2FGaza.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F14161537%2FGaza.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F14161537%2FGaza-300x150.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F14161537%2FGaza-1024x512.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F14161537%2FGaza-800x400.jpg%20800w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-684715%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPalestinians%20inspect%20the%20ruins%20of%20a%20building%20destroyed%20in%20Israeli%20airstrikes%20in%20Khan%20Younis.%20Photo%3A%20Palestinian%20News%20%26amp%3B%20Information%20Agency%20(Wafa)%20in%20contract%20with%20APAimages%2FWikimedia%20Commons.%20CC%20BY-SA%203.0%20Unported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ESuch%20growing%20settler%20impunity%20has%20made%20protective%20presence%20activism%20much%20harder%2C%20with%20activists%20sometimes%20struggling%20even%20to%20enter%20Palestinian%20communities%20because%20of%20physical%20roadblocks%20that%20have%20been%20placed%20to%20obstruct%20the%20way%20in.%20David%20Shulman%2C%20an%20Israeli%20scholar%20and%20longtime%20member%20of%20Ta%E2%80%99ayush%2C%20described%20how%20some%20Israeli%20activists%20were%20accompanying%20Palestinians%20to%20deliver%20medicines%20to%20a%20West%20Bank%20community%20on%20October%2015th%20when%20they%20came%20across%20a%20roadblock%20manned%20by%20armed%20settlers.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20settlers%20stopped%20the%20car%20and%20wanted%20to%20drag%20the%20Palestinians%20out%20of%20it%20and%20beat%20them%20up%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20me.%20While%20in%20this%20case%20an%20army%20officer%20intervened%20to%20prevent%20violence%2C%20such%20intercession%20is%20far%20from%20guaranteed.%20Indeed%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ochaopt.org%2Fcontent%2Fother-mass-displacement-while-eyes-are-gaza-settlers-advance-west-bank-herders%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0to%20the%20United%20Nations%20Office%20for%20the%20Coordination%20of%20Humanitarian%20Affairs%20(OCHA)%2C%20Israeli%20forces%20have%20either%20accompanied%20or%20actively%20supported%20settlers%20in%20nearly%20half%20of%20their%20recent%20attacks%20on%20Palestinians.%20On%20October%2012th%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20settlers%20attacked%20the%20village%20of%20Tuwani%2C%20but%20far%20from%20stopping%20them%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20army%20chatted%20and%20shook%20hands%20with%20the%20settlers%20as%20they%20returned%20to%20their%20outpost%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Eisner%2C%20who%20was%20one%20of%20the%20protective%20presence%20activists%20present%20in%20Tuwani.%20When%20Eisner%20and%20his%20companions%20called%20the%20Israeli%20police%20to%20try%20and%20stop%20the%20settlers%2C%20the%20police%20likewise%20%E2%80%9Ccompletely%20ignored%20%5Bus%5D%20and%20didn%E2%80%99t%20even%20call%20back%2C%E2%80%9D%20Eisner%20recalled.%20Efforts%20to%20use%20filming%20to%20deter%20settlers%20also%20failed%3B%20in%20fact%2C%20the%20settlers%20proved%20their%20indifference%20to%20activist%20scrutiny%20by%20shooting%20in%20the%20direction%20of%20an%20Italian%20activist%20who%20was%20also%20present%20in%20the%20village%20for%20protective%20presence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIn%20addition%20to%20showing%20the%20limits%20of%20protective%20presence%20in%20wartime%20Israel%2FPalestine%2C%20attacks%20like%20the%20kidnapping%20in%20Wadi%20a-Seeq%20and%20the%20shootings%20in%20Tuwani%20have%20also%20had%20a%20chilling%20effect%20on%20activism%20itself.%20In%20the%20days%20following%20these%20two%20incidents%2C%20text%20messages%20began%20circulating%20among%20anti-occupation%20activist%20groups%20suggesting%20that%20the%20scope%20of%20protective%20presence%20activism%20should%20be%20curtailed%20because%20of%20unprecedented%20risks.%20%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99re%20not%20going%20to%20give%20up%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shulman%20said.%20%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99ll%20go%20on%20doing%20whatever%20we%20can%20in%20those%20places%20that%20we%20can%20still%20reach%2C%20and%20we%E2%80%99ll%20take%20the%20risks.%E2%80%9D%20However%2C%20as%20Vardi%20explained%2C%20%E2%80%9Cit%20is%20now%20important%20that%20seasoned%20activists%2C%20or%20those%20with%20connections%20in%20the%20area%2C%20go%20there%2C%20and%20that%20they%20know%20what%20they%20are%20getting%20into.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EWhile%20activists%20might%20be%20forced%20to%20scale%20back%20protective%20presence%20efforts%2C%20settlers%20are%20continuing%20to%20dispossess%20small%2C%20isolated%20Palestinian%20communities%20in%20Area%20C%E2%80%94the%20roughly%2060%25%20of%20the%20West%20Bank%E2%80%99s%20territory%20under%20full%20Israeli%20control.%20Already%2C%20over%20800%20Palestinians%20have%20been%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ochaopt.org%2Fcontent%2Fother-mass-displacement-while-eyes-are-gaza-settlers-advance-west-bank-herders%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edisplaced%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0in%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ochaopt.org%2Fcontent%2Fhostilities-gaza-strip-and-israel-flash-update-43%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esettler%20attacks%20since%20October%207%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0a%20figure%20that%20represents%2043%25%20of%20all%20Palestinians%20displaced%20since%202022.%20Many%20activists%20are%20seeing%20these%20displacements%20happen%20in%20real%20time.%20In%20the%20village%20of%20Ein%20al-Rashash%2C%20for%20example%2C%20round-the-clock%20protective%20presence%20had%20helped%20the%20community%20hold%20on%20to%20their%20land%2C%20but%20eventually%20settler%20violence%20became%20too%20much%20to%20bear.%20In%20mid-October%2C%20the%20residents%E2%80%9418%20families%20consisting%20of%2085%20Palestinians%E2%80%94packed%20most%20of%20their%20belongings%20and%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2F2023%2Foct%2F21%2Fthe-most-successful-land-grab-strategy-since-1967-as-settlers-push-bedouins-off-west-bank-territory%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eleft%20the%20village%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20180%20residents%20of%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Fnews%2F2023%2F10%2F20%2Fsilent-annexation-settlers-dispossess-west-bank-bedouins-amid-israel-war%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWadi%20a-Seeq%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0also%20met%20with%20the%20same%20fate%20despite%20activists%E2%80%99%20protective%20presence%2C%20and%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.btselem.org%2Fsettler_violence%2F20231019_forcible_transfer_of_isolated_communities_and_families_in_area_c_under_the_cover_of_gaza_fighting%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20list%20continues%20to%20grow%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20really%20devastated%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Shulman.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20persevered%20through%20all%20kinds%20of%20violence%20for%20years.%20These%20communities%20are%20friends%20of%20ours.%20To%20watch%20them%20go%20into%20exile%20is%20an%20agony.%20Truly%20an%20agony.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701685851000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F04132858%2Fcorrie5.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fas-israel-ramps-up-military-action-protective-presence-activism-in-palestine-is-no-longer-working%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20protective%20presence%20activism%20has%20not%20been%20enough