20and%20communications%20were%20disrupted%20in%20many%20parts%20of%20Gaza.%20Their%20parents%20had%20been%20%E2%80%9Cdisplaced%20people%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9Cwho%20knew%20their%20children%20were%20in%20the%20hospital%20and%20didn%E2%80%99t%20think%20the%20hospital%20would%20be%20hit%20or%20raided%20by%20the%20occupation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-testid%3D%5C%22drop-cap-letter%5C%22%20data-el%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20thought%20they%20left%20them%20in%20safety.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-testid%3D%5C%22drop-cap-letter%5C%22%20data-el%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%3EQaoud%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20the%20Israeli%20military%20%E2%80%9Cwas%20informed%20there%20were%20cases%E2%80%9D%20left%20inside%20the%20hospital%2C%20but%20%E2%80%9Cwas%20determined%20to%20evacuate%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-testid%3D%5C%22drop-cap-letter%5C%22%20data-el%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%3EDavies%2C%20the%20Red%20Cross%20spokeswoman%2C%20said%20the%20organisation%20%E2%80%9Creceived%20several%20requests%20to%20evacuate%20hospitals%20in%20the%20north%20of%20Gaza%2C%20but%20due%20to%20this%20security%20situation%2C%20we%20were%20not%20involved%20in%20any%20operations%20of%20evacuations%2C%20nor%20did%20teams%20commit%20to%20doing%20so.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-testid%3D%5C%22drop-cap-letter%5C%22%20data-el%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%3ENo%20one%20has%20emerged%20to%20claim%20the%20bodies.%20There%20has%20been%20no%20indication%20that%20the%20parents%20know%20their%20children%20are%20dead%2C%20the%20nurse%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-testid%3D%5C%22drop-cap-letter%5C%22%20data-el%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%3EHe%20remains%20haunted%20by%20the%20event.%20He%20believes%20he%20needs%20psychiatric%20treatment%2C%20the%20daily%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-testid%3D%5C%22drop-cap-letter%5C%22%20data-el%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%3EOf%20what%2C%20he%20asks%2C%20were%20the%20babies%20guilty%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-testid%3D%5C%22d