as%20Mizoram%20Votes%20in%20Zoram%20People's%20Movement%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F04135901%2F401496004_762396555919280_8101576401723065424_n.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20With%20the%20trends%20in%20the%20counting%20of%20votes%20for%20the%20Mizoram%20assembly%20elections%20firming%20up%20on%20Monday%2C%20December%204%2C%20the%20Zoram%20People%E2%80%99s%20Movement%20(ZPM)%20is%20poised%20for%20a%20massive%20victory%20over%20its%20regional%20rival%2C%20the%20Mizo%20National%20Front%20(MNF).%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20per%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20website%2C%20ZPM%20won%2027%20seats%20%E2%80%93%20comfortably%20more%20than%20the%20simple%20majority%20mark%20of%2021%20in%20the%2040-member%20house.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20has%20made%20the%20ZPM%E2%80%99s%20victory%20sweeter%20is%20also%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20candidate%20Lalthansanga%20defeating%20chief%20minister%20and%20MNF%20supremo%20Zoramthanga%20by%202%2C101%20votes%20in%20the%20Aizawl%20East-1%20seat.%20MNF%20looks%20set%20to%20win%2010%20seats%20and%20the%20BJP%20won%202.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Congress%20is%20set%20to%20win%20only%20one%20seat%2C%20the%20Lawngtlai%20West%20seat%20%E2%80%93%20its%20worst%20performance%20in%20recent%20years%20in%20the%20state.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EVoting%20for%20the%20elections%20in%20the%20Northeastern%20state%20was%20held%20in%20a%20single%20phase%20on%20November%207.%20Over%2080%25%20of%20the%20electorate%20participated%20in%20the%20ballot%20that%20saw%20174%20candidates%20in%20the%20fray%2C%20including%2016%20women.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThough%20the%20ECI%20had%20set%20December%203%20as%20the%20date%20for%20the%20counting%20of%20votes%2C%20like%20in%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20four%20states%20that%20voted%20in%20November%2C%20the%20poll%20body%20had%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fec-changes-counting-date-for-mizoram-assembly-polls-to-december-4%5C%22%3Erevise%20the%20date%20to%20December%204%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20poll%20panel%20received%20multiple%20representations%20from%20political%20parties%2C%20the%20Church%20and%20civil%20society%20organisations%20as%20December%203%20was%20a%20Sunday%2C%20the%20holy%20day%20for%20Christians%2C%20a%20majority%20in%20the%20state.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%E2%80%99s%20win%20in%20three%20North%20Indian%20states%20and%20the%20Congress%20taking%20Telangana%20on%20December%203%20has%20already%20set%20the%20tone%20in%20the%20media%20for%20election-related%20deliberations%20and%20stock-taking%2C%20the%20sweep%20of%20ZPM%20in%20a%20tiny%20state%20like%20Mizoram%20is%20also%20noteworthy.%20Here%20are%20eight%20takeaways%20from%20today%E2%80%99s%20Mizoram%20electoral%20results.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20ZPM%E2%80%99s%20win%20means%20Mizoram%20will%20get%20a%20new%20face%20as%20its%20chief%20minister%20in%20Lalduhoma.%20It%20can%20also%20mean%2079-year-old%20Zoramthanga%2C%20a%20stalwart%20in%20Mizo%20politics%20for%20over%20three%20decades%2C%20sailing%20off%20into%20the%20political%20sunset.%20Already%2C%20another%20veteran%20Mizo%20politician%2C%20former%20two-time%20chief%20minister%20Lalthanhawla%2C%20had%20announced%20his%20retirement%20from%20politics%20after%20the%202018%20loss%20of%20his%20Congress%20party.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Today%E2%80%99s%20gigantic%20win%20by%20ZPM%20has%20also%20changed%20the%2035-year-old%20cycle%20of%20MNF%20and%20Congress%20sharing%20power%20in%20the%20border%20state%20alternately.%20After%20the%20signing%20of%20the%20Mizo%20Accord%20with%20the%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20government%20in%201986%2C%20the%20Congress%20government%20under%20Lalthanhawla%20stepped%20down%20from%20the%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20post%20to%20give%20way%20to%20MNF%E2%80%99s%20Laldenga.%20Since%20then%2C%20in%20every%20assembly%20poll%2C%20the%20national%20party%20has%20been%20engaged%20in%20a%20two-corner%20contest%20with%20the%20MNF%20until%20the%20ZPM%20arrived%20on%20the%20scene%20in%20the%202018%20polls%2C%20and%20the%20BJP%20upped%20its%20game%20under%20Narendra%20Modi.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20With%20the%20MNF%20failing%20to%20repeat%20its%202018%20win%20in%20the%20state%2C%20the%20regional%20party%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20break%20the%20cycle%20in%20Mizoram%20of%20a%20party%20failing%20to%20return%20to%20power%20for%20a%20third%20consecutive%20term.%20It%20is%20no%20cakewalk%20for%20any%20party%20to%20sidestep%20anti-incumbency%20and%20return%20to%20power%20for%20a%20third%20term.%20In%20the%20Northeast%2C%20only%20the%20Congress%20under%20the%20chief%20ministership%20of%20Tarun%20Gogoi%20could%20pull%20it%20off%20in%20Assam%20in%202011.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F29124850%2FF05qfKDacAAHNnr.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F29124850%2FF05qfKDacAAHNnr.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F29124850%2FF05qfKDacAAHNnr-300x151.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F29124850%2FF05qfKDacAAHNnr-1024x514.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F29124850%2FF05qfKDacAAHNnr-800x400.jpeg%20800w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-677473%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22602%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EMizoram%20chief%20minister%20Zoramthanga.%20Photo%3A%20X%20(Twitter)%20%2F%40ZoramthangaCM%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20December%204%20election%20results%20that%20threw%20up%20two%20wins%20for%20the%20BJP%20have%20underlined%20that%20its%20footprint%20in%20Mizoram%20is%20growing.%20However%2C%20it%20also%20holds%20up%20that%2C%20once%20again%2C%20the%20national%20party%20failed%20to%20have%20an%20MLA%20in%20the%20state%20from%20the%20majority%20Mizo%20community.%20This%20was%20even%20after%20the%20assembly%20speaker%20from%20the%20MNF%2C%20Lalrinliana%2C%20had%20shifted%20base%20to%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20these%20elections.%20This%20makes%20Mizoram%20the%20only%20state%20where%20BJP%20has%20failed%20to%20enter%20a%20north-eastern%20state%E2%80%99s%20majority%20community%20in%20spite%20of%20being%20in%20power%20in%20New%20Delhi.%20In%20all%2C%20the%20BJP%20contested%2023%20seats.%20Only%20five%20of%20its%20candidates%20were%20non-Mizos.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Today%E2%80%99s%20verdict%20has%20also%20shown%20that%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20entry%20into%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20Mara%20community%20has%20further%20firmed%20up.%20While%20the%20party%20candidate%20K.%20Hrahmo%20won%20the%20Palak%20seat%2C%20K.%20Beichhua%2C%20a%20former%20senior%20minister%20of%20the%20MNF%20who%20also%20recently%20moved%20to%20the%20BJP%2C%20picked%20up%20the%20Siaha%20seat%20for%20the%20party.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20two%20wins%20for%20the%20BJP%20came%20soon%20after%20its%20sweep%20of%20the%20Mara%20District%20Council%20in%20Mizoram.%20In%202017%2C%20the%20Mara%20Democratic%20Front%20merged%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20gave%20the%20national%20party%20a%20much-needed%20entry%20into%20the%20Mara%20community%2C%20the%20second%20most%20influential%20community%20after%20the%20Mizos.%20In%202019%2C%20that%20move%20helped%20the%20BJP%20grab%20the%20Mara%20District%20Council.%20This%20past%20April%2C%20the%20BJP%20swept%20the%20Council%20elections.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3E6.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20BJP%20losing%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3Ethe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcan-the-bjp-emerge-as-kingmaker-in-mizoram-as-pollsters-predict-a-hung-assembly%5C%22%3ETuichawng%20constituency%3C%2Fa%3E%20suggests%20that%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20hold%20in%202018%20over%20the%20Chakma%20community%20in%20Mizoram%20was%20most%20likely%20due%20to%20the%20popularity%20of%20its%20then-candidate%20Budha%20Dhan%20Chakma.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBudha%20Dhan%20Chakma%2C%20a%20former%20minister%20in%20the%20Lalthanhawla%20government%2C%20had%20moved%20to%20the%20BJP%20close%20to%20the%202018%20elections%20and%20went%20on%20to%20give%20the%20party%20its%20first%20taste%20of%20victory%20in%20Mizoram%E2%80%99s%20assembly%20elections.%20This%20time%20around%2C%20Budha%20Dhan%20had%20announced%20his%20retirement%20from%20politics%2C%20leading%20the%20BJP%20to%20bank%20on%20a%20new%20candidate%2C%20Durjya%C2%A0%20Dhan%20Chakma.%20He%20lost%20to%20MNF%E2%80%99s%20Rasik%20Mohan%20Chakma.%20Like%20in%20the%20Mara%20Council%2C%20the%20BJP%20had%20also%20succeeded%20in%20capturing%20the%20Chakma%20District%20Council%20of%20Mizoram%2C%20a%20strategy%20it%20had%20adopted%20some%20years%20ago%20to%20enter%20the%20Mizoram%20election%20fray.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20in%20the%20recent%20polls%2C%20today%E2%80%99s%20winner%20from%20the%20MNF%2C%20Rasik%20Mohan%20Chakma%2C%20became%20its%20chief%20executive%20member.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3E7.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20MNF%E2%80%99s%20failure%20to%20hold%20on%20to%20power%20also%20means%20that%20the%20Mizos%20did%20not%20consider%20the%20ethnic%20strife%20in%20Manipur%20that%20had%20affected%20their%20kindred%20community%2C%20the%20Kukis%2C%20as%20an%20election%20issue.%20The%20voters%20rather%20bit%20into%20the%20ZPM%E2%80%99s%20stand%20during%20the%20campaigning%20that%20the%20Manipur%20issue%20is%20important%20to%20all%20Zo%20people%20and%20their%20politicians%20across%20party%20lines.%20Though%20Zoramthanga%20had%20stridently%20batted%20for%20the%20Kukis%2C%20and%20also%20for%20the%20displaced%20Chins%20of%20Myanmar%2C%20and%20tried%20tilting%20it%20into%20an%20election%20issue%2C%20the%20voters%20didn%E2%80%99t%20look%20at%20him%20as%20the%20only%20Mizo%20leader%20who%20can%20continue%20that%20support%20to%20their%20kindred%20lot.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3E8.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Finally%2C%20while%20ZPM%E2%80%99s%20win%20has%20meant%20the%20rise%20of%20a%20new%20regional%20party%20in%20Mizoram%20after%20the%20MNF%2C%20the%20phenomenon%20is%2C%20but%2C%20only%20a%20second%20across%20the%20Northeast%20in%20recent%20times.%20In%20the%20last%20Nagaland%20elections%2C%20one%20saw%20a%20new%20regional%20party%2C%20the%20Nationalist%20Democratic%20People%E2%80%99s%20Party%20(NDPP)%2C%20seizing%20power%20from%20an%20already%20entrenched%20regional%20entity%2C%20the%20Naga%20People%E2%80%99s%20Front%20(NPF).%20Like%20the%20MNF%2C%20the%20NPF%20was%20also%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20first%20regional%20party%20to%20have%20grabbed%20power%20from%20the%20Congress%20in%20spite%20of%20the%20national%20party%20being%20well%20entrenched%20at%20the%20Centre%20and%20in%20most%20of%20the%20Northeast.%20Like%20the%20MNF%2C%20the%20NPF%20was%20also%20a%20BJP%20ally.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20NPF%2C%20ditto%20MNF%20in%20Mizoram%2C%20had%20resisted%20sharing%20power%20with%20the%20BJP%20in%20Nagaland%2C%20the%20NDPP%E2%80%99s%20win%20in%20Nagaland%20made%20way%20for%20the%20BJP%20to%20enter%20the%20state%20government%20not%20only%20for%20the%20first%20time%20but%20to%20also%20demand%20plum%20portfolios%20like%20that%20of%20the%20state%20home%20ministry.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EToday%2C%20even%20as%20counting%20was%20ongoing%20in%20Mizoram%2C%20the%20BJP%20state%20president%20Vanlalhmuaka%20told%20reporters%20that%20his%20party%20%E2%80%9Cwill%20participate%20in%20the%20new%20government%20which%20will%20be%20formed%20soon.%E2%80%9D%20Since%20the%20ZPM%20is%20seen%20as%20close%20to%20the%20BJP%2C%20his%20statement%20could%20well%20be%20true.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20it%20does%2C%20it%20could%20be%20termed%20as%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20effective%20%E2%80%98Nagaland%20model%E2%80%99%20for%20the%20Christian-majority%20states%20in%20the%20Northeast.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701679513000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F04135901%2F401496004_762396555919280_8101576401723065424_n.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmizoram-eight-takeaways-zpm-mnf-bjp%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22What%20has%20made%20the%20ZPM%E2%80%99s%20victory%20sweeter%20is%20also%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20candidate%20Lalthansanga%20defeating%20chief%20minister%20and%20MNF%20supremo%20Zoramthanga%20by%202%2C101%20votes%20in%20the%20Aizawl%20East-1%20seat.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmizoram-eight-takeaways-zpm-mnf-bjp%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Crimes%20Against%20Women%20and%20Children%2C%20Suicides%2C%20Sudden%20Deaths%20Increased%20in%202022%3A%20NCRB%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F02%2F18224008%2Fmax-kleinen-ugdKmhDg1m8-unsplash.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20National%20Crime%20Records%20Bureau%20(NCRB)%20released%20the%20annual%20crime%20report%2C%20and%20the%20Accidental%20Deaths%20and%20Suicides%20in%20India%20(ADSI)%20report%2C%20on%20Sunday%2C%C2%A0December%203%2C%20when%20the%20results%20of%20the%20Assembly%20elections%20in%20four%20states%20were%20announced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20it%20was%20published%20in%20August.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fcrimes-against-women-children-scst-and-cyber-crimes-increased-in-2022-crime-in-india-report%2Farticle67602315.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EHindu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20report%20provides%20a%20comprehensive%20overview%20of%20the%20crime%20scenario%20in%20India%20in%202022%2C%20including%20the%20number%20of%20sudden%20deaths%2C%20suicides%2C%20crimes%20against%20women%2C%20children%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20overall%20crime%20rate%20declined%20from%207%25%20in%202021%20to%206.9%25%20in%202022%2C%20the%20newspaper%20reported%2C%20citing%20the%20NCRB%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20crimes%20against%20specific%20categories%2C%20including%20women%2C%20children%2C%20SC%2C%20ST%2C%20and%20cyber%20crimes%2C%20increased%20compared%20to%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESudden%20deaths%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20an%2011.6%25%20increase%20in%20the%20number%20of%20%E2%80%9Csudden%20deaths%E2%80%9D%20reported%20across%20the%20country%2C%20the%20ADSI%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20least%2056%2C653%20sudden%20deaths%20were%20reported%20in%202022%2C%20with%20heart%20attacks%20accounting%20for%2032%2C410%20deaths.%20Other%20reasons%20were%20attributed%20for%2024%2C243%20deaths.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20age%20group%20of%2045-60%20years%20reported%20the%20maximum%20number%20of%20deaths%20(19%2C456).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20study%20by%20the%20Indian%20Council%20of%20Medical%20Research%20and%20Registrar%20General%20of%20India%2C%20India%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fmagazines%2Fpanache%2Fcardiovascular-diseases-killing-indians-the-most-pulmonary-embolism-rheumatic-condition-and-other-heart-disorders-people-should-know-about%2Farticleshow%2F94509483.cms%5C%22%3Eaccounts%20for%20approximately%2060%25%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20heart%20disease%20burden.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESuicides%20and%20accidental%20deaths%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuicides%20increased%20to%201%2C70%2C924%20in%202022%20compared%20to%201%2C64%2C033%20in%202021%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccidental%20deaths%20also%20increased%20to%204%2C30%2C504%20in%202022%20compared%20to%203%2C97%2C530%20in%202021%2C%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiaspend.com%2Fdata-gaps%2Fis-indias-highest-suicide-rate-because-of-better-reporting-or-rising-distress-836959%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EIndiaSpend%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20India%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fncrb.gov.in%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2FADSI-2021%2FADSI_2021_FULL_REPORT.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ereported%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20highest%20suicide%20rate%20in%20its%20history%20in%202021%2C%20with%2012%20suicides%20for%20every%20100%2C000%20people.%20But%20the%20numbers%20could%20be%20higher.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20September%202022%2C%20a%20psychiatrist%20had%20told%20%3Cem%3EIndiaSpend%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethat%20there%20are%20several%20reasons%20why%20India%20might%20be%20underreporting%20suicides.%20These%20are%20lack%20of%20medical%20certification%20of%20deaths%2C%20stigma%20associated%20with%20mental%20health%2C%20and%20criminalisation%2C%20not%20just%20in%20terms%20of%20reporting%20of%20sucides%20but%20sometimes%20also%20in%20the%20denial%20of%20insurance%20if%20the%20death%20is%20by%20suicide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECrimes%20against%20women%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20least%204%2C45%2C256%20cases%20of%20%E2%80%98crimes%20against%20women%E2%80%99%20were%20registered%20in%202022%2C%20showing%20a%204%25%20increase%20from%202021%2C%20the%20newspaper%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMajor%20cases%20included%20cruelty%20by%20husband%20or%20his%20relatives%2C%20kidnapping%20and%20abduction%20of%20women%2C%20assault%20on%20women%20with%20intent%20to%20outrage%20her%20modesty%2C%20and%20rape.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-india-62830634%5C%22%3E2022%20%3Cem%3EBBC%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20citing%20the%20World%20Health%20Organization%2C%20said%20that%20one%20in%20three%20women%20globally%20face%20gender-based%20violence%20and%20the%20numbers%20for%20India%20are%20similar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20noted%20that%20India%20recorded%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20crimes%20against%20women%20ever%20in%202021.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20rise%20of%2026.35%25%20over%20six%20years%20since%202016.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECrimes%20against%20children%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20least%201%2C62%2C449%20cases%20of%20crimes%20against%20children%20were%20registered%20in%202022%2C%20reflecting%20an%208.7%25%20increase%20from%202021%2C%20the%20daily%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKidnapping%20and%20abduction%20and%20crimes%20under%20the%20Protection%20of%20Children%20from%20Sexual%20Offences%20(POCSO)%20Act%20were%20prominent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOther%20crimes%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECrimes%20against%20senior%20citizens%2C%20Scheduled%20Castes%20(SC)%2C%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20(ST)%2C%20and%20economic%20offences%20showed%20a%20massive%20increase.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20total%20of%2028%2C545%20cases%20were%20registered%20for%20committing%20crimes%20against%20senior%20citizens%20(above%2060%20years)%2C%20showing%20an%20increase%20of%209.3%25%20over%202021%20(26%2C110%20cases)%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20newspaper%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20total%20of%2057%2C582%20cases%20were%20registered%20for%20committing%20crimes%20against%20SCs%2C%20showing%20an%20in